"use strict";(self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi=self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi||[]).push([[224],{224:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('[{"pageId":1,"rawText":"Yirmi Birinci S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0130ki makamd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirinci Makam\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0648\u0629\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0643\u0650\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0648\u062a\u064b\u0627\\n\\nBir zaman sinnen, cismen, r\xfctbeten b\xfcy\xfck bir adam bana dedi: \u201cNamaz iyidir. Fakat her g\xfcn her g\xfcn be\u015fer defa k\u0131lmak \xe7oktur. Bitmedi\u011finden usan\xe7 veriyor.\u201d\\n\\nO zat\u0131n o s\xf6z\xfcnden hayli zaman ge\xe7tikten sonra, nefsimi dinledim. \u0130\u015fittim ki ayn\u0131 s\xf6zleri s\xf6yl\xfcyor ve ona bakt\u0131m g\xf6rd\xfcm ki tembellik kula\u011f\u0131yla \u015feytandan ayn\u0131 dersi al\u0131yor. O vakit anlad\u0131m o zat o s\xf6z\xfc, b\xfct\xfcn n\xfcfus-u emmarenin nam\u0131na s\xf6ylemi\u015f gibidir veya s\xf6ylettirilmi\u015ftir. O zaman ben dahi dedim: \u201cMadem nefsim emmaredir. Nefsini \u0131slah etmeyen, ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 \u0131slah edemez. \xd6yle ise nefsimden ba\u015flar\u0131m.\u201d\\n\\nDedim: Ey nefis! Cehl-i m\xfcrekkeb i\xe7inde, tembellik d\xf6\u015fe\u011finde, gaflet uykusunda s\xf6yledi\u011fin \u015fu s\xf6ze mukabil be\u015f ikaz\u0131 benden i\u015fit.\\n\\nBirinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy bedbaht nefsim! Acaba \xf6mr\xfcn ebed\xee midir? Hi\xe7 kat\u2019\xee senedin var m\u0131 ki gelecek seneye belki yar\u0131na kadar kalacaks\u0131n? Sana usan\xe7 veren, tevehh\xfcm-\xfc ebediyettir. Keyif i\xe7in ebed\xee d\xfcnyada kalacak gibi nazlan\u0131yorsun. E\u011fer anlasa idin ki \xf6mr\xfcn azd\u0131r hem faydas\u0131z gidiyor. Elbette onun yirmi d\xf6rtten birisini, hakiki bir hayat-\u0131 ebediyenin saadetine medar olacak bir g\xfczel ve ho\u015f ve rahat ve rahmet bir hizmete sarf etmek; usanmak \u015f\xf6yle dursun, belki ciddi bir i\u015ftiyak ve ho\u015f bir zevki tahrike sebep olur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy \u015fikem-perver nefsim! Acaba her g\xfcn her g\xfcn ekmek yersin, su i\xe7ersin, havay\u0131 teneff\xfcs edersin; sana onlar usan\xe7 veriyor mu? Madem vermiyor \xe7\xfcnk\xfc ihtiya\xe7 tekerr\xfcr etti\u011finden usan\xe7 de\u011fil belki telezz\xfcz ediyorsun. \xd6yle ise hane-i cismimde senin arkada\u015flar\u0131n olan kalbimin g\u0131das\u0131, ruhumun \xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131 ve lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniyemin hava-y\u0131 nes\xeemini cezb ve celbeden namaz dahi seni usand\u0131rmamak gerektir.\\n\\nEvet, nihayetsiz teess\xfcrat ve elemlere maruz ve m\xfcptela ve nihayetsiz telezz\xfczata ve emellere meftun ve p\xfcr-sevda bir kalbin kut ve kuvveti, her \u015feye k\u0101dir bir Rah\xeem-i Ker\xeem\u2019in kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 niyaz ile \xe7almakla elde edilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, \u015fu f\xe2ni d\xfcnyada kemal-i s\xfcratle vaveyl\xe2-y\u0131 firak\u0131 koparan giden ekser mevcudatla al\xe2kadar bir ruhun \xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131 ise her \u015feye bedel bir Mabud-u B\xe2ki\u2019nin, bir Mahbub-u Sermed\xee\u2019nin \xe7e\u015fme-i rahmetine namaz ile tevecc\xfch etmekle i\xe7ilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, f\u0131traten ebediyeti isteyen ve ebed i\xe7in halk olunan ve ezel\xee ve ebed\xee bir zat\u0131n \xe2yinesi olan ve nihayetsiz derecede nazik ve letafetli bulunan z\xee\u015fuur bir s\u0131rr-\u0131 insan\xee, z\xeenur bir lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniye; \u015fu kasavetli, ezici ve s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131, ge\xe7ici ve zul\xfcmatl\u0131 ve bo\u011fucu olan ahval-i d\xfcnyeviye i\xe7inde, elbette teneff\xfcse pek \xe7ok muhta\xe7t\u0131r ve ancak namaz\u0131n penceresiyle nefes alabilir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Acaba ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet k\xfclfetini ve namaz\u0131n me\u015fakkatini ve musibet zahmetini, bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp muzdarip olmak hem gelecek g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet vazifesini ve namaz hizmetini ve musibet elemini, bug\xfcn tasavvur edip sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131k g\xf6stermek hi\xe7 k\xe2r-\u0131 ak\u0131l m\u0131d\u0131r?\\n\\n\u015eu sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131kta misalin \u015f\xf6yle bir sersem kumandana benzer ki: D\xfc\u015fman\u0131n sa\u011f cenah kuvveti onun sa\u011f\u0131ndaki kuvvetine iltihak etmi\u015f ve ona taze bir kuvvet oldu\u011fu halde; o tutar m\xfchim bir kuvvetini sa\u011f cenaha g\xf6nderir, merkezi zay\u0131fla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. Hem sol cenahta d\xfc\u015fman\u0131n askeri yok iken ve daha gelmeden, b\xfcy\xfck bir kuvvet g\xf6nderir \u201cAte\u015f et!\u201d emrini verir. Merkezi b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn kuvvetten d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. D\xfc\u015fman i\u015fi anlar, merkeze h\xfccum eder, t\xe2rumar eder.","modernText":"Yirmi Birinci S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0130ki makamd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirinci Makam\\n\\n[[Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|]]\\n\\n[[Namaz m\xfcminler \xfczerine vakitleri belli olarak yaz\u0131l\u0131 bir farzd\u0131r.|\u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u0670\u0648\u0629\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0643\u0650\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0648\u062a\u064b\u0627|Nisa Suresi, 103. Ayet]]\\n\\nBir zaman [[ya\u015f\xe7a|sinnen|]], [[bedence|cismen|]], [[makamca|r\xfctbeten|]] b\xfcy\xfck bir adam bana dedi: \u201cNamaz iyidir. Fakat her g\xfcn her g\xfcn be\u015fer defa k\u0131lmak \xe7oktur. Bitmedi\u011finden usan\xe7 veriyor.\u201d\\n\\nO zat\u0131n o s\xf6z\xfcnden hayli zaman ge\xe7tikten sonra, nefsimi dinledim. \u0130\u015fittim ki ayn\u0131 s\xf6zleri s\xf6yl\xfcyor ve ona bakt\u0131m g\xf6rd\xfcm ki tembellik kula\u011f\u0131yla \u015feytandan ayn\u0131 dersi al\u0131yor. O vakit anlad\u0131m o zat o s\xf6z\xfc, b\xfct\xfcn [[k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emreden nefislerin|n\xfcfus-u emmarenin|]] [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] s\xf6ylemi\u015f gibidir veya s\xf6ylettirilmi\u015ftir. O zaman ben dahi dedim: \u201cMadem nefsim [[k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emredendir|emmaredir|]]. Nefsini [[d\xfczeltmeyen/iyile\u015ftirmeyen|\u0131slah etmeyen|]], ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 [[d\xfczeltemez|\u0131slah edemez|]]. \xd6yle ise nefsimden ba\u015flar\u0131m.\u201d\\n\\nDedim: Ey nefis! [[koyu cehalet/bilmedi\u011fini de bilmemek|Cehl-i m\xfcrekkeb|]] i\xe7inde, tembellik d\xf6\u015fe\u011finde, gaflet uykusunda s\xf6yledi\u011fin \u015fu s\xf6ze [[kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k|mukabil|]] be\u015f [[uyar\u0131y\u0131|ikaz\u0131|]] benden i\u015fit.\\n\\nBirinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[talihsiz/mutsuz|bedbaht|]] nefsim! Acaba \xf6mr\xfcn ebed\xee midir? Hi\xe7 [[kesin|kat\u2019\xee|]] [[belgen/kan\u0131t\u0131n|senedin|]] var m\u0131 ki gelecek seneye belki yar\u0131na kadar kalacaks\u0131n? Sana usan\xe7 veren, [[sonsuz ya\u015fayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 sanmakt\u0131r/ebedilik kuruntusudur|tevehh\xfcm-\xfc ebediyettir|]]. Keyif i\xe7in ebed\xee d\xfcnyada kalacak gibi nazlan\u0131yorsun. E\u011fer anlasa idin ki \xf6mr\xfcn azd\u0131r hem faydas\u0131z gidiyor. Elbette onun yirmi d\xf6rtten birisini, [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] bir [[sonsuz hayat\u0131n|hayat-\u0131 ebediyenin|]] [[mutlulu\u011funa|saadetine|]] [[sebep olacak/kaynak olacak|medar olacak|]] bir g\xfczel ve ho\u015f ve rahat ve rahmet bir hizmete [[harcamak|sarf etmek|]]; usanmak \u015f\xf6yle dursun, belki ciddi bir [[g\xfc\xe7l\xfc istek/arzu|i\u015ftiyak|]] ve ho\u015f bir zevki [[harekete ge\xe7irmeye/uyand\u0131rmaya|tahrike|]] sebep olur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[midesine d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn/bo\u011faz\u0131na d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn|\u015fikem-perver|]] nefsim! Acaba her g\xfcn her g\xfcn ekmek yersin, su i\xe7ersin, havay\u0131 [[solursun|teneff\xfcs edersin|]]; sana onlar usan\xe7 veriyor mu? Madem vermiyor \xe7\xfcnk\xfc ihtiya\xe7 [[tekrarland\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan/yenilendi\u011finden|tekerr\xfcr etti\u011finden|]] usan\xe7 de\u011fil belki [[lezzet al\u0131yorsun|telezz\xfcz ediyorsun|]]. \xd6yle ise [[beden evimde|hane-i cismimde|]] senin arkada\u015flar\u0131n olan kalbimin g\u0131das\u0131, ruhumun [[hayat suyu/can suyu|\xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131|]] ve [[ilahi duygumun/Rabbani latifemin|lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniyemin|]] [[tatl\u0131 esintisini/ho\u015f havas\u0131n\u0131|hava-y\u0131 nes\xeemini|]] [[\xe7eken ve getiren|cezb ve celbeden|]] namaz dahi seni usand\u0131rmamak gerektir.\\n\\nEvet, [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] [[\xfcz\xfcnt\xfcler|teess\xfcrat|]] ve elemlere maruz ve [[tutulmu\u015f|m\xfcptela|]] ve [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] [[lezzetlere/zevklenmelere|telezz\xfczata|]] ve [[arzulara|emellere|]] [[tutkun/vurgun|meftun|]] ve [[sevda dolu/a\u015fk dolu|p\xfcr-sevda|]] bir kalbin [[g\u0131das\u0131/az\u0131\u011f\u0131|kut|]] ve kuvveti, her \u015feye [[g\xfcc\xfc yeten|k\u0101dir|]] bir [[sonsuz merhamet ve c\xf6mertlik sahibi Allah\'\u0131n|Rah\xeem-i Ker\xeem\u2019in|]] kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 [[yalvarma/dua|niyaz|]] ile \xe7almakla elde edilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, \u015fu [[ge\xe7ici|f\xe2ni|]] d\xfcnyada [[tam bir h\u0131zla|kemal-i s\xfcratle|]] [[ayr\u0131l\u0131k \xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131|vaveyl\xe2-y\u0131 firak\u0131|]] koparan giden [[\xe7o\u011fu|ekser|]] [[varl\u0131klarla|mevcudatla|]] [[ilgili/ba\u011fl\u0131|al\xe2kadar|]] bir ruhun [[hayat suyu|\xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131|]] ise her \u015feye [[kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k/yerine ge\xe7en|bedel|]] bir [[sonsuz \u0130badet Edilen\'in|Mabud-u B\xe2ki\u2019nin|]], bir [[ebedi Sevgili\'nin|Mahbub-u Sermed\xee\u2019nin|]] [[rahmet \xe7e\u015fmesine|\xe7e\u015fme-i rahmetine|]] namaz ile [[y\xf6nelmekle|tevecc\xfch etmekle|]] i\xe7ilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, [[yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f\xe7a/do\u011fas\u0131 gere\u011fi|f\u0131traten|]] [[sonsuzlu\u011fu|ebediyeti|]] isteyen ve [[sonsuzluk|ebed|]] i\xe7in [[yarat\u0131lan|halk olunan|]] ve ezel\xee ve ebed\xee bir [[zat\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)|zat\u0131n|]] [[aynas\u0131|\xe2yinesi|]] olan ve [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] derecede nazik ve [[latif/ince|letafetli|]] bulunan [[\u015fuur sahibi/bilin\xe7li|z\xee\u015fuur|]] bir [[insanl\u0131k s\u0131rr\u0131|s\u0131rr-\u0131 insan\xee|]], [[nurlu/\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131|z\xeenur|]] bir [[Rabbani duygu|lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniye|]]; \u015fu [[s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131/kederli|kasavetli|]], ezici ve s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131, ge\xe7ici ve [[karanl\u0131kl\u0131|zul\xfcmatl\u0131|]] ve bo\u011fucu olan [[d\xfcnya halleri|ahval-i d\xfcnyeviye|]] i\xe7inde, elbette [[nefes almaya|teneff\xfcse|]] pek \xe7ok muhta\xe7t\u0131r ve ancak namaz\u0131n penceresiyle nefes alabilir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Acaba ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet [[zorlu\u011funu/y\xfck\xfcn\xfc|k\xfclfetini|]] ve namaz\u0131n [[zahmetini|me\u015fakkatini|]] ve musibet zahmetini, bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp [[ac\u0131 \xe7ekmek/\u0131st\u0131rap duymak|muzdarip olmak|]] hem gelecek g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet vazifesini ve namaz hizmetini ve musibet elemini, bug\xfcn [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp/hayal edip|tasavvur edip|]] sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131k g\xf6stermek hi\xe7 [[ak\u0131l k\xe2r\u0131/ak\u0131ll\u0131ca i\u015f|k\xe2r-\u0131 ak\u0131l|]] m\u0131d\u0131r?\\n\\n\u015eu sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131kta [[\xf6rne\u011fin|misalin|]] \u015f\xf6yle bir sersem kumandana benzer ki: D\xfc\u015fman\u0131n [[sa\u011f kanat|sa\u011f cenah|]] kuvveti onun sa\u011f\u0131ndaki kuvvetine [[kat\u0131lm\u0131\u015f|iltihak etmi\u015f|]] ve ona taze bir kuvvet oldu\u011fu halde; o tutar [[\xf6nemli|m\xfchim|]] bir kuvvetini [[sa\u011f kanada|sa\u011f cenaha|]] g\xf6nderir, merkezi zay\u0131fla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. Hem [[sol kanatta|sol cenahta|]] d\xfc\u015fman\u0131n askeri yok iken ve daha gelmeden, b\xfcy\xfck bir kuvvet g\xf6nderir \u201cAte\u015f et!\u201d emrini verir. Merkezi b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn kuvvetten d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. D\xfc\u015fman i\u015fi anlar, merkeze h\xfccum eder, [[darmada\u011f\u0131n eder/yok eder|t\xe2rumar eder|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:31","oldText":"Yirmi Birinci S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0130ki makamd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirinci Makam\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[\u0627\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u0670\u0648\u0629\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0643\u0650\u062a\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0648\u062a\u064b\u0627|Namaz m\xfcminler \xfczerine vakitleri belli olarak yaz\u0131l\u0131 bir farzd\u0131r.|Nisa Suresi, 103. Ayet]]\\n\\nBir zaman [[sinnen|ya\u015f\xe7a]], [[cismen|bedence]], [[r\xfctbeten|makamca]] b\xfcy\xfck bir adam bana dedi: \u201cNamaz iyidir. Fakat her g\xfcn her g\xfcn be\u015fer defa k\u0131lmak \xe7oktur. Bitmedi\u011finden usan\xe7 veriyor.\u201d\\n\\nO zat\u0131n o s\xf6z\xfcnden hayli zaman ge\xe7tikten sonra, nefsimi dinledim. \u0130\u015fittim ki ayn\u0131 s\xf6zleri s\xf6yl\xfcyor ve ona bakt\u0131m g\xf6rd\xfcm ki tembellik kula\u011f\u0131yla \u015feytandan ayn\u0131 dersi al\u0131yor. O vakit anlad\u0131m o zat o s\xf6z\xfc, b\xfct\xfcn [[n\xfcfus-u emmarenin|k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emreden nefislerin]] [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] s\xf6ylemi\u015f gibidir veya s\xf6ylettirilmi\u015ftir. O zaman ben dahi dedim: \u201cMadem nefsim [[emmaredir|k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emredendir]]. Nefsini [[\u0131slah etmeyen|d\xfczeltmeyen/iyile\u015ftirmeyen]], ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 [[\u0131slah edemez|d\xfczeltemez]]. \xd6yle ise nefsimden ba\u015flar\u0131m.\u201d\\n\\nDedim: Ey nefis! [[Cehl-i m\xfcrekkeb|koyu cehalet/bilmedi\u011fini de bilmemek]] i\xe7inde, tembellik d\xf6\u015fe\u011finde, gaflet uykusunda s\xf6yledi\u011fin \u015fu s\xf6ze [[mukabil|kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k]] be\u015f [[ikaz\u0131|uyar\u0131y\u0131]] benden i\u015fit.\\n\\nBirinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[bedbaht|talihsiz/mutsuz]] nefsim! Acaba \xf6mr\xfcn ebed\xee midir? Hi\xe7 [[kat\u2019\xee|kesin]] [[senedin|belgen/kan\u0131t\u0131n]] var m\u0131 ki gelecek seneye belki yar\u0131na kadar kalacaks\u0131n? Sana usan\xe7 veren, [[tevehh\xfcm-\xfc ebediyettir|sonsuz ya\u015fayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 sanmakt\u0131r/ebedilik kuruntusudur]]. Keyif i\xe7in ebed\xee d\xfcnyada kalacak gibi nazlan\u0131yorsun. E\u011fer anlasa idin ki \xf6mr\xfcn azd\u0131r hem faydas\u0131z gidiyor. Elbette onun yirmi d\xf6rtten birisini, [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] bir [[hayat-\u0131 ebediyenin|sonsuz hayat\u0131n]] [[saadetine|mutlulu\u011funa]] [[medar olacak|sebep olacak/kaynak olacak]] bir g\xfczel ve ho\u015f ve rahat ve rahmet bir hizmete [[sarf etmek|harcamak]]; usanmak \u015f\xf6yle dursun, belki ciddi bir [[i\u015ftiyak|g\xfc\xe7l\xfc istek/arzu]] ve ho\u015f bir zevki [[tahrike|harekete ge\xe7irmeye/uyand\u0131rmaya]] sebep olur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[\u015fikem-perver|midesine d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn/bo\u011faz\u0131na d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn]] nefsim! Acaba her g\xfcn her g\xfcn ekmek yersin, su i\xe7ersin, havay\u0131 [[teneff\xfcs edersin|solursun]]; sana onlar usan\xe7 veriyor mu? Madem vermiyor \xe7\xfcnk\xfc ihtiya\xe7 [[tekerr\xfcr etti\u011finden|tekrarland\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan/yenilendi\u011finden]] usan\xe7 de\u011fil belki [[telezz\xfcz ediyorsun|lezzet al\u0131yorsun]]. \xd6yle ise [[hane-i cismimde|beden evimde]] senin arkada\u015flar\u0131n olan kalbimin g\u0131das\u0131, ruhumun [[\xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131|hayat suyu/can suyu]] ve [[lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniyemin|ilahi duygumun/Rabbani latifemin]] [[hava-y\u0131 nes\xeemini|tatl\u0131 esintisini/ho\u015f havas\u0131n\u0131]] [[cezb ve celbeden|\xe7eken ve getiren]] namaz dahi seni usand\u0131rmamak gerektir.\\n\\nEvet, [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] [[teess\xfcrat|\xfcz\xfcnt\xfcler]] ve elemlere maruz ve [[m\xfcptela|tutulmu\u015f]] ve [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] [[telezz\xfczata|lezzetlere/zevklenmelere]] ve [[emellere|arzulara]] [[meftun|tutkun/vurgun]] ve [[p\xfcr-sevda|sevda dolu/a\u015fk dolu]] bir kalbin [[kut|g\u0131das\u0131/az\u0131\u011f\u0131]] ve kuvveti, her \u015feye [[k\u0101dir|g\xfcc\xfc yeten]] bir [[Rah\xeem-i Ker\xeem\u2019in|sonsuz merhamet ve c\xf6mertlik sahibi Allah\'\u0131n]] kap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 [[niyaz|yalvarma/dua]] ile \xe7almakla elde edilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, \u015fu [[f\xe2ni|ge\xe7ici]] d\xfcnyada [[kemal-i s\xfcratle|tam bir h\u0131zla]] [[vaveyl\xe2-y\u0131 firak\u0131|ayr\u0131l\u0131k \xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131]] koparan giden [[ekser|\xe7o\u011fu]] [[mevcudatla|varl\u0131klarla]] [[al\xe2kadar|ilgili/ba\u011fl\u0131]] bir ruhun [[\xe2b-\u0131 hayat\u0131|hayat suyu]] ise her \u015feye [[bedel|kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k/yerine ge\xe7en]] bir [[Mabud-u B\xe2ki\u2019nin|sonsuz \u0130badet Edilen\'in]], bir [[Mahbub-u Sermed\xee\u2019nin|ebedi Sevgili\'nin]] [[\xe7e\u015fme-i rahmetine|rahmet \xe7e\u015fmesine]] namaz ile [[tevecc\xfch etmekle|y\xf6nelmekle]] i\xe7ilebilir.\\n\\nEvet, [[f\u0131traten|yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f\xe7a/do\u011fas\u0131 gere\u011fi]] [[ebediyeti|sonsuzlu\u011fu]] isteyen ve [[ebed|sonsuzluk]] i\xe7in [[halk olunan|yarat\u0131lan]] ve ezel\xee ve ebed\xee bir [[zat\u0131n|zat\u0131n (Allah\'\u0131n)]] [[\xe2yinesi|aynas\u0131]] olan ve [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] derecede nazik ve [[letafetli|latif/ince]] bulunan [[z\xee\u015fuur|\u015fuur sahibi/bilin\xe7li]] bir [[s\u0131rr-\u0131 insan\xee|insanl\u0131k s\u0131rr\u0131]], [[z\xeenur|nurlu/\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131]] bir [[lat\xeefe-i Rabbaniye|Rabbani duygu]]; \u015fu [[kasavetli|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131/kederli]], ezici ve s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131, ge\xe7ici ve [[zul\xfcmatl\u0131|karanl\u0131kl\u0131]] ve bo\u011fucu olan [[ahval-i d\xfcnyeviye|d\xfcnya halleri]] i\xe7inde, elbette [[teneff\xfcse|nefes almaya]] pek \xe7ok muhta\xe7t\u0131r ve ancak namaz\u0131n penceresiyle nefes alabilir.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Acaba ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet [[k\xfclfetini|zorlu\u011funu/y\xfck\xfcn\xfc]] ve namaz\u0131n [[me\u015fakkatini|zahmetini]] ve musibet zahmetini, bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp [[muzdarip olmak|ac\u0131 \xe7ekmek/\u0131st\u0131rap duymak]] hem gelecek g\xfcnlerdeki ibadet vazifesini ve namaz hizmetini ve musibet elemini, bug\xfcn [[tasavvur edip|d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp/hayal edip]] sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131k g\xf6stermek hi\xe7 [[k\xe2r-\u0131 ak\u0131l|ak\u0131l k\xe2r\u0131/ak\u0131ll\u0131ca i\u015f]] m\u0131d\u0131r?\\n\\n\u015eu sab\u0131rs\u0131zl\u0131kta [[misalin|\xf6rne\u011fin]] \u015f\xf6yle bir sersem kumandana benzer ki: D\xfc\u015fman\u0131n [[sa\u011f cenah|sa\u011f kanat]] kuvveti onun sa\u011f\u0131ndaki kuvvetine [[iltihak etmi\u015f|kat\u0131lm\u0131\u015f]] ve ona taze bir kuvvet oldu\u011fu halde; o tutar [[m\xfchim|\xf6nemli]] bir kuvvetini [[sa\u011f cenaha|sa\u011f kanada]] g\xf6nderir, merkezi zay\u0131fla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. Hem [[sol cenahta|sol kanatta]] d\xfc\u015fman\u0131n askeri yok iken ve daha gelmeden, b\xfcy\xfck bir kuvvet g\xf6nderir \u201cAte\u015f et!\u201d emrini verir. Merkezi b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn kuvvetten d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. D\xfc\u015fman i\u015fi anlar, merkeze h\xfccum eder, [[t\xe2rumar eder|darmada\u011f\u0131n eder/yok eder]]."},{"pageId":2,"rawText":"Evet, buna benzersin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerin zahmeti, bug\xfcn rahmete kalbolmu\u015f; elemi gitmi\u015f, lezzeti kalm\u0131\u015f. K\xfclfeti, keramete iltihak ve me\u015fakkati, sevaba ink\u0131lab etmi\u015f. \xd6yle ise ondan usan\xe7 almak de\u011fil belki yeni bir \u015fevk, taze bir zevk ve devama ciddi bir gayret almak l\xe2z\u0131m gelir. Gelecek g\xfcnler ise madem gelmemi\u015fler. \u015eimdiden d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp usanmak ve f\xfctur getirmek aynen o g\xfcnlerde a\xe7l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve susuzlu\u011fu ile bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp ba\u011f\u0131r\u0131p \xe7a\u011f\u0131rmak gibi bir divaneliktir.\\n\\nMadem hakikat b\xf6yledir. \xc2k\u0131l isen ibadet cihetinde yaln\u0131z bug\xfcn\xfc d\xfc\u015f\xfcn ve onun bir saatini, \xfccreti pek b\xfcy\xfck, k\xfclfeti pek az, ho\u015f ve g\xfczel ve ulvi bir hizmete sarf ediyorum, de. O vakit senin ac\u0131 bir f\xfcturun, tatl\u0131 bir gayrete ink\u0131lab eder.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Sen \xfc\xe7 sab\u0131r ile m\xfckellefsin.\\n\\nBirisi: Taat \xfcst\xfcnde sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirisi: Masiyetten sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri: Musibete kar\u015f\u0131 sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nAkl\u0131n varsa \u015fu \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc ikazdaki temsilde g\xf6r\xfcnen hakikati rehber tut. Merdane \u201cY\xe2 Sab\xfbr!\u201d de, \xfc\xe7 sabr\u0131 omuzuna al. Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n sana verdi\u011fi sab\u0131r kuvvetini, e\u011fer yanl\u0131\u015f yolda da\u011f\u0131tmazsan her me\u015fakkate ve her musibete k\xe2fi gelebilir ve o kuvvetle dayan.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sersem nefsim! Acaba \u015fu vazife-i ubudiyet neticesiz midir, \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r ki sana usan\xe7 veriyor? Halbuki bir adam sana birka\xe7 para verse veyahut seni korkutsa ak\u015fama kadar seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ve f\xfctursuz \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rs\u0131n.\\n\\nAcaba bu misafirhane-i d\xfcnyada \xe2ciz ve fakir kalbine kut ve g\u0131na ve elbette bir menzilin olan kabrinde g\u0131da ve ziya ve herhalde mahkemen olan mah\u015ferde senet ve berat ve ister istemez \xfcst\xfcnden ge\xe7ilecek s\u0131rat k\xf6pr\xfcs\xfcnde nur ve burak olacak bir namaz, neticesiz midir veyahut \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r? Bir adam sana y\xfcz liral\u0131k bir hediye vaad etse y\xfcz g\xfcn seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. Hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad edebilir o adama itimat edersin, f\xfctursuz i\u015flersin.\\n\\nAcaba hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad, hakk\u0131nda muhal olan bir zat, cennet gibi bir \xfccreti ve saadet-i ebediye gibi bir hediyeyi sana vaad etse pek az bir zamanda, pek g\xfczel bir vazifede seni istihdam etse; sen hizmet etmezsen veya isteksiz, suhre gibi veya usan\xe7la, yar\u0131m yamalak hizmetinle onu vaadinde ittiham ve hediyesini istihfaf etsen pek \u015fiddetli bir te\u2019dibe ve deh\u015fetli bir tazibe m\xfcstahak olaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnm\xfcyor musun? D\xfcnyada hapsin korkusundan en a\u011f\u0131r i\u015flerde f\xfctursuz hizmet etti\u011fin halde; cehennem gibi bir haps-i ebed\xeenin havf\u0131, en hafif ve lat\xeef bir hizmet i\xe7in sana gayret vermiyor mu?\\n\\nBe\u015finci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy d\xfcnya-perest nefsim! Acaba ibadetteki f\xfcturun ve namazdaki kusurun me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviyenin kesretinden midir veyahut derd-i mai\u015fetin me\u015fgalesiyle vakit bulamad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan m\u0131d\u0131r? Acaba s\u0131rf d\xfcnya i\xe7in mi yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015fs\u0131n ki b\xfct\xfcn vaktini ona sarf ediyorsun!\\n\\nSen istidat cihetiyle b\xfct\xfcn hayvanat\u0131n fevkinde oldu\u011funu ve hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131 tedarikte iktidar cihetiyle, bir ser\xe7e ku\u015funa yeti\u015femedi\u011fini biliyorsun. Bundan neden anlam\u0131yorsun ki vazife-i asliyen hayvan gibi \xe7abalamak de\u011fil, belki hakiki bir insan gibi hakiki bir hayat-\u0131 daime i\xe7in sa\u2019y etmektir.\\n\\nBununla beraber me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviye dedi\u011fin, \xe7o\u011fu sana ait olmayan ve fuzul\xee bir surette kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131n ve kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131n malayani me\u015fgalelerdir. En elzemini b\u0131rak\u0131p g\xfcya binler sene \xf6mr\xfcn var gibi en l\xfczumsuz mal\xfbmat ile vakit ge\xe7iriyorsun. Mesela, \u201cZ\xfchal\u2019in etraf\u0131ndaki halkalar\u0131n keyfiyeti nas\u0131ld\u0131r?\u201d ve \u201cAmerika tavuklar\u0131 ne kadard\u0131r?\u201d gibi k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerle k\u0131ymettar vaktini ge\xe7iriyorsun. G\xfcya kozmo\u011frafya ilminden ve istatistik\xe7i fenninden bir kemal al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: \u201cBeni namazdan ve ibadetten al\u0131koyan ve f\xfctur veren \xf6yle l\xfczumsuz \u015feyler de\u011fil, belki derd-i mai\u015fetin zarur\xee i\u015fleridir.\u201d","modernText":"Evet, buna benzersin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerin zahmeti, bug\xfcn [[merhamete/nime|rahmete|]] [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f/\xe7evrilmi\u015f|kalbolmu\u015f|]]; [[ac\u0131s\u0131/kederi|elemi|]] gitmi\u015f, [[tad\u0131/zevki|lezzeti|]] kalm\u0131\u015f. [[Zorlu\u011fu/Y\xfck\xfc|K\xfclfeti|]], [[ikrama/l\xfctfa|keramete|]] [[kat\u0131lma|iltihak|]] ve [[zahmeti/zorlu\u011fu|me\u015fakkati|]], sevaba [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f/ba\u015fkala\u015fm\u0131\u015f|ink\u0131lab etmi\u015f|]]. \xd6yle ise ondan usan\xe7 almak de\u011fil [[aksine/bilakis|belki|]] yeni bir [[istek/arzu|\u015fevk|]], taze bir zevk ve devama ciddi bir gayret almak [[gerekir|l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|]]. Gelecek g\xfcnler ise madem gelmemi\u015fler. \u015eimdiden d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp usanmak ve [[gev\u015feklik g\xf6stermek/bezginlik getirmek|f\xfctur getirmek|]] aynen o g\xfcnlerde a\xe7l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve susuzlu\u011fu ile bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp ba\u011f\u0131r\u0131p \xe7a\u011f\u0131rmak gibi bir [[deliliktir/ak\u0131ls\u0131zl\u0131kt\u0131r|divaneliktir|]].\\n\\nMadem [[ger\xe7ek|hakikat|]] b\xf6yledir. [[Ak\u0131ll\u0131|\xc2k\u0131l|]] isen ibadet [[y\xf6n\xfcnde/taraf\u0131nda|cihetinde|]] yaln\u0131z bug\xfcn\xfc d\xfc\u015f\xfcn ve onun bir saatini, \xfccreti pek b\xfcy\xfck, [[zorlu\u011fu/zahmeti|k\xfclfeti|]] pek az, ho\u015f ve g\xfczel ve [[y\xfcce/y\xfcksek|ulvi|]] bir hizmete [[harc\u0131yorum|sarf ediyorum|]], de. O vakit senin ac\u0131 bir [[gev\u015fekli\u011fin/bezginli\u011fin|f\xfcturun|]], tatl\u0131 bir gayrete [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcr|ink\u0131lab eder|]].\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Sen \xfc\xe7 sab\u0131r ile [[y\xfck\xfcml\xfcs\xfcn/sorumlusun|m\xfckellefsin|]].\\n\\nBirisi: [[\u0130badet/\u0130taat|Taat|]] \xfcst\xfcnde sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirisi: [[G\xfcnahtan/\u0130taatsizlikten|Masiyetten|]] sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri: [[Felakete/Belaya|Musibete|]] kar\u015f\u0131 sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nAkl\u0131n varsa \u015fu \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[uyar\u0131daki|ikazdaki|]] [[\xf6rnekte/k\u0131yasta|temsilde|]] g\xf6r\xfcnen [[ger\xe7e\u011fi|hakikati|]] rehber tut. [[Mert\xe7e/Yi\u011fit\xe7e|Merdane|]] \u201c[[Ey \xe7ok sab\u0131rl\u0131 olan (Allah)|Y\xe2 Sab\xfbr|]]!\u201d de, \xfc\xe7 sabr\u0131 omuzuna al. [[Y\xfcce Allah\'\u0131n|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n|]] sana verdi\u011fi sab\u0131r kuvvetini, e\u011fer yanl\u0131\u015f yolda da\u011f\u0131tmazsan her [[zorlu\u011fa/zahmete|me\u015fakkate|]] ve her [[belaya/felakete|musibete|]] [[yeterli gelebilir|k\xe2fi gelebilir|]] ve o kuvvetle dayan.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sersem nefsim! Acaba \u015fu [[kulluk g\xf6revi|vazife-i ubudiyet|]] [[sonu\xe7suz|neticesiz|]] midir, \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r ki sana usan\xe7 veriyor? Halbuki bir adam sana birka\xe7 para verse veyahut seni korkutsa ak\u015fama kadar seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ve [[bezginlik g\xf6stermeden/gev\u015femeden|f\xfctursuz|]] \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rs\u0131n.\\n\\nAcaba bu [[d\xfcnya misafirhanesinde|misafirhane-i d\xfcnyada|]] [[g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz|\xe2ciz|]] ve fakir kalbine [[az\u0131k/g\u0131da|kut|]] ve [[zenginlik|g\u0131na|]] ve elbette bir [[dura\u011f\u0131n/yerin|menzilin|]] olan kabrinde g\u0131da ve [[\u0131\u015f\u0131k|ziya|]] ve herhalde mahkemen olan [[k\u0131yamet g\xfcn\xfcnde toplanma yerinde|mah\u015ferde|]] senet ve [[kurtulu\u015f belgesi|berat|]] ve ister istemez \xfcst\xfcnden ge\xe7ilecek s\u0131rat k\xf6pr\xfcs\xfcnde nur ve [[binek (cennet bine\u011fi)|burak|]] olacak bir namaz, [[sonu\xe7suz|neticesiz|]] midir veyahut \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r? Bir adam sana y\xfcz liral\u0131k bir hediye [[s\xf6z verse|vaad etse|]] y\xfcz g\xfcn seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. [[S\xf6z\xfcnden d\xf6nebilir|Hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad edebilir|]] o adama [[g\xfcvenirsin|itimat edersin|]], [[usan\xe7 duymadan/gev\u015femeden|f\xfctursuz|]] i\u015flersin.\\n\\nAcaba [[s\xf6z\xfcnden d\xf6nme|hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad|]], hakk\u0131nda [[imkans\u0131z|muhal|]] olan bir zat, cennet gibi bir \xfccreti ve [[sonsuz mutluluk|saadet-i ebediye|]] gibi bir hediyeyi sana [[s\xf6z verse|vaad etse|]] pek az bir zamanda, pek g\xfczel bir vazifede seni [[\xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsa|istihdam etse|]]; sen hizmet etmezsen veya isteksiz, [[angarya/zoraki i\u015f|suhre|]] gibi veya usan\xe7la, yar\u0131m yamalak hizmetinle onu vaadinde [[su\xe7lama|ittiham|]] ve hediyesini [[k\xfc\xe7\xfcmsesen/hafife alsan|istihfaf etsen|]] pek \u015fiddetli bir [[edeplendirmeye/cezaland\u0131rmaya|te\u2019dibe|]] ve deh\u015fetli bir [[azapland\u0131rmaya/azaba|tazibe|]] [[hak etmi\u015f|m\xfcstahak|]] olaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnm\xfcyor musun? D\xfcnyada hapsin korkusundan en a\u011f\u0131r i\u015flerde [[bezginlik duymadan|f\xfctursuz|]] hizmet etti\u011fin halde; cehennem gibi bir [[sonsuz hapsin|haps-i ebed\xeenin|]] [[korkusu|havf\u0131|]], en hafif ve [[ho\u015f/nazik|lat\xeef|]] bir hizmet i\xe7in sana gayret vermiyor mu?\\n\\nBe\u015finci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[d\xfcnyaya tapan/d\xfcnyay\u0131 \xe7ok seven|d\xfcnya-perest|]] nefsim! Acaba ibadetteki [[gev\u015fekli\u011fin/usanc\u0131n|f\xfcturun|]] ve namazdaki kusurun [[d\xfcnya i\u015flerinin/me\u015fguliyetlerinin|me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviyenin|]] [[\xe7oklu\u011fundan|kesretinden|]] midir veyahut [[ge\xe7im derdinin|derd-i mai\u015fetin|]] [[u\u011fra\u015f\u0131s\u0131yla|me\u015fgalesiyle|]] vakit bulamad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan m\u0131d\u0131r? Acaba s\u0131rf d\xfcnya i\xe7in mi yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015fs\u0131n ki b\xfct\xfcn vaktini ona [[harc\u0131yorsun|sarf ediyorsun|]]!\\n\\nSen [[yetenek/kabiliyet|istidat|]] [[y\xf6n\xfcyle|cihetiyle|]] b\xfct\xfcn hayvanat\u0131n [[\xfcst\xfcnde|fevkinde|]] oldu\u011funu ve [[d\xfcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131n|hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin|]] [[gere\xe7lerini/ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131|levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|]] [[elde etmede|tedarikte|]] [[g\xfc\xe7/yapabilme|iktidar|]] [[y\xf6n\xfcyle|cihetiyle|]], bir ser\xe7e ku\u015funa yeti\u015femedi\u011fini biliyorsun. Bundan neden anlam\u0131yorsun ki [[as\u0131l g\xf6revin|vazife-i asliyen|]] hayvan gibi \xe7abalamak de\u011fil, [[bilakis/aksine|belki|]] [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] bir insan gibi [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] bir [[sonsuz hayat/ebedi hayat|hayat-\u0131 daime|]] i\xe7in [[\xe7al\u0131\u015fmakt\u0131r|sa\u2019y etmektir|]].\\n\\nBununla beraber [[d\xfcnya i\u015fleri/u\u011fra\u015flar\u0131|me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviye|]] dedi\u011fin, \xe7o\u011fu sana ait olmayan ve [[gereksiz/bo\u015f yere|fuzul\xee|]] bir [[bi\xe7imde/\u015fekilde|surette|]] kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131n ve kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131n [[bo\u015f/anlams\u0131z|malayani|]] me\u015fgalelerdir. En [[en gerekli olan\u0131n\u0131|elzemini|]] b\u0131rak\u0131p g\xfcya binler sene \xf6mr\xfcn var gibi en l\xfczumsuz [[bilgiler|mal\xfbmat|]] ile vakit ge\xe7iriyorsun. Mesela, \u201c[[Sat\xfcrn\'\xfcn|Z\xfchal\u2019in|]] etraf\u0131ndaki halkalar\u0131n [[niteli\u011fi/durumu|keyfiyeti|]] nas\u0131ld\u0131r?\u201d ve \u201cAmerika tavuklar\u0131 ne kadard\u0131r?\u201d gibi k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerle [[de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymettar|]] vaktini ge\xe7iriyorsun. G\xfcya [[g\xf6k bilimi/astronomi|kozmo\u011frafya|]] ilminden ve istatistik\xe7i [[biliminden|fenninden|]] bir [[olgunluk/bilgi|kemal|]] al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: \u201cBeni namazdan ve ibadetten al\u0131koyan ve [[gev\u015feklik veren/usan\xe7 veren|f\xfctur veren|]] \xf6yle l\xfczumsuz \u015feyler de\u011fil, [[bilakis/aksine|belki|]] [[ge\xe7im derdinin|derd-i mai\u015fetin|]] [[zorunlu|zarur\xee|]] i\u015fleridir.\u201d","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:32","oldText":"Evet, buna benzersin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc ge\xe7mi\u015f g\xfcnlerin zahmeti, bug\xfcn [[rahmete|merhamete/nime]] [[kalbolmu\u015f|d\xf6n\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f/\xe7evrilmi\u015f]]; [[elemi|ac\u0131s\u0131/kederi]] gitmi\u015f, [[lezzeti|tad\u0131/zevki]] kalm\u0131\u015f. [[K\xfclfeti|Zorlu\u011fu/Y\xfck\xfc]], [[keramete|ikrama/l\xfctfa]] [[iltihak|kat\u0131lma]] ve [[me\u015fakkati|zahmeti/zorlu\u011fu]], sevaba [[ink\u0131lab etmi\u015f|d\xf6n\xfc\u015fm\xfc\u015f/ba\u015fkala\u015fm\u0131\u015f]]. \xd6yle ise ondan usan\xe7 almak de\u011fil [[belki|aksine/bilakis]] yeni bir [[\u015fevk|istek/arzu]], taze bir zevk ve devama ciddi bir gayret almak [[l\xe2z\u0131m gelir|gerekir]]. Gelecek g\xfcnler ise madem gelmemi\u015fler. \u015eimdiden d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp usanmak ve [[f\xfctur getirmek|gev\u015feklik g\xf6stermek/bezginlik getirmek]] aynen o g\xfcnlerde a\xe7l\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve susuzlu\u011fu ile bug\xfcn d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcp ba\u011f\u0131r\u0131p \xe7a\u011f\u0131rmak gibi bir [[divaneliktir|deliliktir/ak\u0131ls\u0131zl\u0131kt\u0131r]].\\n\\nMadem [[hakikat|ger\xe7ek]] b\xf6yledir. [[\xc2k\u0131l|Ak\u0131ll\u0131]] isen ibadet [[cihetinde|y\xf6n\xfcnde/taraf\u0131nda]] yaln\u0131z bug\xfcn\xfc d\xfc\u015f\xfcn ve onun bir saatini, \xfccreti pek b\xfcy\xfck, [[k\xfclfeti|zorlu\u011fu/zahmeti]] pek az, ho\u015f ve g\xfczel ve [[ulvi|y\xfcce/y\xfcksek]] bir hizmete [[sarf ediyorum|harc\u0131yorum]], de. O vakit senin ac\u0131 bir [[f\xfcturun|gev\u015fekli\u011fin/bezginli\u011fin]], tatl\u0131 bir gayrete [[ink\u0131lab eder|d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcr]].\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey sab\u0131rs\u0131z nefsim! Sen \xfc\xe7 sab\u0131r ile [[m\xfckellefsin|y\xfck\xfcml\xfcs\xfcn/sorumlusun]].\\n\\nBirisi: [[Taat|\u0130badet/\u0130taat]] \xfcst\xfcnde sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nBirisi: [[Masiyetten|G\xfcnahtan/\u0130taatsizlikten]] sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nDi\u011feri: [[Musibete|Felakete/Belaya]] kar\u015f\u0131 sab\u0131rd\u0131r.\\n\\nAkl\u0131n varsa \u015fu \xfc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[ikazdaki|uyar\u0131daki]] [[temsilde|\xf6rnekte/k\u0131yasta]] g\xf6r\xfcnen [[hakikati|ger\xe7e\u011fi]] rehber tut. [[Merdane|Mert\xe7e/Yi\u011fit\xe7e]] \u201c[[Y\xe2 Sab\xfbr|Ey \xe7ok sab\u0131rl\u0131 olan (Allah)]]!\u201d de, \xfc\xe7 sabr\u0131 omuzuna al. [[Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019\u0131n|Y\xfcce Allah\'\u0131n]] sana verdi\u011fi sab\u0131r kuvvetini, e\u011fer yanl\u0131\u015f yolda da\u011f\u0131tmazsan her [[me\u015fakkate|zorlu\u011fa/zahmete]] ve her [[musibete|belaya/felakete]] [[k\xe2fi gelebilir|yeterli gelebilir]] ve o kuvvetle dayan.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy sersem nefsim! Acaba \u015fu [[vazife-i ubudiyet|kulluk g\xf6revi]] [[neticesiz|sonu\xe7suz]] midir, \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r ki sana usan\xe7 veriyor? Halbuki bir adam sana birka\xe7 para verse veyahut seni korkutsa ak\u015fama kadar seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ve [[f\xfctursuz|bezginlik g\xf6stermeden/gev\u015femeden]] \xe7al\u0131\u015f\u0131rs\u0131n.\\n\\nAcaba bu [[misafirhane-i d\xfcnyada|d\xfcnya misafirhanesinde]] [[\xe2ciz|g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz]] ve fakir kalbine [[kut|az\u0131k/g\u0131da]] ve [[g\u0131na|zenginlik]] ve elbette bir [[menzilin|dura\u011f\u0131n/yerin]] olan kabrinde g\u0131da ve [[ziya|\u0131\u015f\u0131k]] ve herhalde mahkemen olan [[mah\u015ferde|k\u0131yamet g\xfcn\xfcnde toplanma yerinde]] senet ve [[berat|kurtulu\u015f belgesi]] ve ister istemez \xfcst\xfcnden ge\xe7ilecek s\u0131rat k\xf6pr\xfcs\xfcnde nur ve [[burak|binek (cennet bine\u011fi)]] olacak bir namaz, [[neticesiz|sonu\xe7suz]] midir veyahut \xfccreti az m\u0131d\u0131r? Bir adam sana y\xfcz liral\u0131k bir hediye [[vaad etse|s\xf6z verse]] y\xfcz g\xfcn seni \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r. [[Hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad edebilir|S\xf6z\xfcnden d\xf6nebilir]] o adama [[itimat edersin|g\xfcvenirsin]], [[f\xfctursuz|usan\xe7 duymadan/gev\u015femeden]] i\u015flersin.\\n\\nAcaba [[hulf\xfc\u2019l-vaad|s\xf6z\xfcnden d\xf6nme]], hakk\u0131nda [[muhal|imkans\u0131z]] olan bir zat, cennet gibi bir \xfccreti ve [[saadet-i ebediye|sonsuz mutluluk]] gibi bir hediyeyi sana [[vaad etse|s\xf6z verse]] pek az bir zamanda, pek g\xfczel bir vazifede seni [[istihdam etse|\xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsa]]; sen hizmet etmezsen veya isteksiz, [[suhre|angarya/zoraki i\u015f]] gibi veya usan\xe7la, yar\u0131m yamalak hizmetinle onu vaadinde [[ittiham|su\xe7lama]] ve hediyesini [[istihfaf etsen|k\xfc\xe7\xfcmsesen/hafife alsan]] pek \u015fiddetli bir [[te\u2019dibe|edeplendirmeye/cezaland\u0131rmaya]] ve deh\u015fetli bir [[tazibe|azapland\u0131rmaya/azaba]] [[m\xfcstahak|hak etmi\u015f]] olaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnm\xfcyor musun? D\xfcnyada hapsin korkusundan en a\u011f\u0131r i\u015flerde [[f\xfctursuz|bezginlik duymadan]] hizmet etti\u011fin halde; cehennem gibi bir [[haps-i ebed\xeenin|sonsuz hapsin]] [[havf\u0131|korkusu]], en hafif ve [[lat\xeef|ho\u015f/nazik]] bir hizmet i\xe7in sana gayret vermiyor mu?\\n\\nBe\u015finci \u0130kaz\\n\\nEy [[d\xfcnya-perest|d\xfcnyaya tapan/d\xfcnyay\u0131 \xe7ok seven]] nefsim! Acaba ibadetteki [[f\xfcturun|gev\u015fekli\u011fin/usanc\u0131n]] ve namazdaki kusurun [[me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviyenin|d\xfcnya i\u015flerinin/me\u015fguliyetlerinin]] [[kesretinden|\xe7oklu\u011fundan]] midir veyahut [[derd-i mai\u015fetin|ge\xe7im derdinin]] [[me\u015fgalesiyle|u\u011fra\u015f\u0131s\u0131yla]] vakit bulamad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan m\u0131d\u0131r? Acaba s\u0131rf d\xfcnya i\xe7in mi yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015fs\u0131n ki b\xfct\xfcn vaktini ona [[sarf ediyorsun|harc\u0131yorsun]]!\\n\\nSen [[istidat|yetenek/kabiliyet]] [[cihetiyle|y\xf6n\xfcyle]] b\xfct\xfcn hayvanat\u0131n [[fevkinde|\xfcst\xfcnde]] oldu\u011funu ve [[hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin|d\xfcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131n]] [[levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|gere\xe7lerini/ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131]] [[tedarikte|elde etmede]] [[iktidar|g\xfc\xe7/yapabilme]] [[cihetiyle|y\xf6n\xfcyle]], bir ser\xe7e ku\u015funa yeti\u015femedi\u011fini biliyorsun. Bundan neden anlam\u0131yorsun ki [[vazife-i asliyen|as\u0131l g\xf6revin]] hayvan gibi \xe7abalamak de\u011fil, [[belki|bilakis/aksine]] [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] bir insan gibi [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] bir [[hayat-\u0131 daime|sonsuz hayat/ebedi hayat]] i\xe7in [[sa\u2019y etmektir|\xe7al\u0131\u015fmakt\u0131r]].\\n\\nBununla beraber [[me\u015f\xe2gil-i d\xfcnyeviye|d\xfcnya i\u015fleri/u\u011fra\u015flar\u0131]] dedi\u011fin, \xe7o\u011fu sana ait olmayan ve [[fuzul\xee|gereksiz/bo\u015f yere]] bir [[surette|bi\xe7imde/\u015fekilde]] kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131n ve kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131\u011f\u0131n [[malayani|bo\u015f/anlams\u0131z]] me\u015fgalelerdir. En [[elzemini|en gerekli olan\u0131n\u0131]] b\u0131rak\u0131p g\xfcya binler sene \xf6mr\xfcn var gibi en l\xfczumsuz [[mal\xfbmat|bilgiler]] ile vakit ge\xe7iriyorsun. Mesela, \u201c[[Z\xfchal\u2019in|Sat\xfcrn\'\xfcn]] etraf\u0131ndaki halkalar\u0131n [[keyfiyeti|niteli\u011fi/durumu]] nas\u0131ld\u0131r?\u201d ve \u201cAmerika tavuklar\u0131 ne kadard\u0131r?\u201d gibi k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerle [[k\u0131ymettar|de\u011ferli]] vaktini ge\xe7iriyorsun. G\xfcya [[kozmo\u011frafya|g\xf6k bilimi/astronomi]] ilminden ve istatistik\xe7i [[fenninden|biliminden]] bir [[kemal|olgunluk/bilgi]] al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: \u201cBeni namazdan ve ibadetten al\u0131koyan ve [[f\xfctur veren|gev\u015feklik veren/usan\xe7 veren]] \xf6yle l\xfczumsuz \u015feyler de\u011fil, [[belki|bilakis/aksine]] [[derd-i mai\u015fetin|ge\xe7im derdinin]] [[zarur\xee|zorunlu]] i\u015fleridir.\u201d"},{"pageId":3,"rawText":"\xd6yle ise ben de sana derim ki: E\u011fer y\xfcz kuru\u015f bir g\xfcndelik ile \xe7al\u0131\u015fsan sonra biri gelse, dese ki: \u201cGel on dakika kadar \u015furay\u0131 kaz, y\xfcz lira k\u0131ymetinde bir p\u0131rlanta ve bir z\xfcmr\xfct bulacaks\u0131n.\u201d Sen ona: \u201cYok, gelmem. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc on kuru\u015f g\xfcndeli\u011fimden kesilecek, nafakam azalacak.\u201d desen, ne kadar divanece bir bahane oldu\u011funu elbette bilirsin.\\n\\nAynen onun gibi sen \u015fu ba\u011f\u0131nda, nafakan i\xe7in i\u015fliyorsun. E\u011fer farz namaz\u0131 terk etsen b\xfct\xfcn sa\u2019yin semeresi, yaln\u0131z d\xfcnyev\xee ve ehemmiyetsiz ve bereketsiz bir nafakaya m\xfcnhas\u0131r kal\u0131r. E\u011fer sen istirahat ve teneff\xfcs vaktini, ruhun rahat\u0131na, kalbin teneff\xfcs\xfcne medar olan namaza sarf etsen o vakit, bereketli nafaka-i d\xfcnyeviye ile beraber, senin nafaka-i uhreviyene ve z\xe2d-\u0131 \xe2hiretine ehemmiyetli bir menba olan, iki maden-i manev\xee bulursun:\\n\\nBirinci maden: B\xfct\xfcn ba\u011f\u0131ndaki (H\xe2\u015fiye[1]) yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fin \u2013\xe7i\xe7ekli olsun, meyveli olsun\u2013 her nebat\u0131n, her a\u011fac\u0131n tesbihat\u0131ndan, g\xfczel bir niyet ile bir hisse al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\n\u0130kinci maden: Hem bu ba\u011fdan \xe7\u0131kan mahsulattan kim yese \u2013hayvan olsun, insan olsun; inek olsun, sinek olsun; m\xfc\u015fteri olsun, h\u0131rs\u0131z olsun\u2013 sana bir sadaka h\xfckm\xfcne ge\xe7er. Fakat o \u015fart ile ki sen, Rezzak-\u0131 Hakiki nam\u0131na ve izni dairesinde tasarruf etsen ve onun mal\u0131n\u0131, onun mahlukat\u0131na veren bir tevziat memuru nazar\u0131yla kendine baksan\u2026\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bak, namaz\u0131 terk eden ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir hasaret eder, ne kadar ehemmiyetli bir serveti kaybeder ve sa\u2019ye pek b\xfcy\xfck bir \u015fevk veren ve amelde b\xfcy\xfck bir kuvve-i manev\xee temin eden o iki neticeden ve o iki madenden mahrum kal\u0131r, iflas eder. Hatt\xe2 ihtiyarland\u0131k\xe7a bah\xe7ecilikten usan\u0131r, f\xfctur gelir. \u201cNeme l\xe2z\u0131m.\u201d der. \u201cBen zaten d\xfcnyadan gidiyorum. Bu kadar zahmeti ne i\xe7in \xe7ekece\u011fim?\u201d diyecek, kendini tembelli\u011fe atacak. Fakat evvelki adam der: \u201cDaha ziyade ibadetle beraber sa\u2019y-i hel\xe2le \xe7al\u0131\u015faca\u011f\u0131m. T\xe2 kabrime daha ziyade \u0131\u015f\u0131k g\xf6nderece\u011fim, \xe2hiretime daha ziyade zah\xeere tedarik edece\u011fim.\u201d\\n\\nElhas\u0131l: Ey nefis! Bil ki d\xfcnk\xfc g\xfcn senin elinden \xe7\u0131kt\u0131. Yar\u0131n ise senin elinde senet yok ki ona m\xe2liksin. \xd6yle ise hakiki \xf6mr\xfcn\xfc, bulundu\u011fun g\xfcn bil. L\xe2ekall g\xfcn\xfcn bir saatini, ihtiyat ak\xe7esi gibi hakiki istikbal i\xe7in te\u015fkil olunan bir sanduk\xe7a-i uhreviye olan bir mescide veya bir seccadeye at.\\n\\nHem bil ki her yeni g\xfcn, sana hem herkese, bir yeni \xe2lemin kap\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r. E\u011fer namaz k\u0131lmazsan senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemin zul\xfcmatl\u0131 ve peri\u015fan bir halde gider, senin aleyhinde \xe2lem-i misalde \u015fehadet eder. Zira herkesin, her g\xfcnde, \u015fu \xe2lemden bir mahsus \xe2lemi var. Hem o \xe2lemin keyfiyeti, o adam\u0131n kalbine ve ameline tabidir. Nas\u0131l ki \xe2yinende g\xf6r\xfcnen muhte\u015fem bir saray, \xe2yinenin rengine bakar. Siyah ise siyah g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 ise k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. Hem onun keyfiyetine bakar. O \xe2yine \u015fi\u015fesi d\xfczg\xfcn ise saray\u0131 g\xfczel g\xf6sterir. D\xfczg\xfcn de\u011fil ise \xe7irkin g\xf6sterir. En nazik \u015feyleri kaba g\xf6sterdi\u011fi misill\xfc sen kalbinle, akl\u0131nla, amelinle, g\xf6nl\xfcnle, kendi \xe2leminin \u015feklini de\u011fi\u015ftirirsin. Ya aleyhinde ya lehinde \u015fehadet ettirebilirsin.\\n\\nE\u011fer namaz\u0131 k\u0131lsan o namaz\u0131n ile o \xe2lemin S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019ine m\xfcteveccih olsan birden, sana bakan \xe2lemin tenevv\xfcr eder. \xc2deta namaz\u0131n bir elektrik lambas\u0131 ve namaza niyetin, onun d\xfc\u011fmesine dokunmas\u0131 gibi o \xe2lemin zul\xfcmat\u0131n\u0131 da\u011f\u0131t\u0131r ve o herc \xfc merc-i d\xfcnyeviyedeki karmakar\u0131\u015f\u0131k peri\u015faniyet i\xe7indeki tebedd\xfclat ve harek\xe2t, hikmetli bir intizam ve manidar bir kitabet-i kudret oldu\u011funu g\xf6sterir. \u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f \u0646\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650 \xe2yet-i p\xfcr-envar\u0131ndan bir nuru, senin kalbine serper. Senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemini, o nurun in\u2019ikas\u0131yla \u0131\u015f\u0131kland\u0131r\u0131r. Senin lehinde nuraniyetle \u015fehadet ettirir.","modernText":"\xd6yle ise ben de sana derim ki: E\u011fer y\xfcz kuru\u015f bir g\xfcndelik ile \xe7al\u0131\u015fsan sonra biri gelse, dese ki: \u201cGel on dakika kadar \u015furay\u0131 kaz, y\xfcz lira [[de\u011ferinde|k\u0131ymetinde|]] bir p\u0131rlanta ve bir z\xfcmr\xfct bulacaks\u0131n.\u201d Sen ona: \u201cYok, gelmem. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc on kuru\u015f g\xfcndeli\u011fimden kesilecek, [[ge\xe7im param/yiyecek param|nafakam|]] azalacak.\u201d desen, ne kadar [[delice/ak\u0131ls\u0131zca|divanece|]] bir bahane oldu\u011funu elbette bilirsin.\\n\\nAynen onun gibi sen \u015fu ba\u011f\u0131nda, [[ge\xe7imin/yiyece\u011fin|nafakan|]] i\xe7in i\u015fliyorsun. E\u011fer farz namaz\u0131 [[b\u0131raksan/terk etsen|terk etsen|]] b\xfct\xfcn [[\xe7al\u0131\u015fman\u0131n/eme\u011fin|sa\u2019yin|]] [[meyvesi/sonucu|semeresi|]], yaln\u0131z [[d\xfcnyaya ait|d\xfcnyev\xee|]] ve [[\xf6nemsiz|ehemmiyetsiz|]] ve bereketsiz bir [[ge\xe7imli\u011fe/r\u0131zka|nafakaya|]] [[s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 kal\u0131r/\xf6zg\xfc kal\u0131r|m\xfcnhas\u0131r kal\u0131r|]]. E\u011fer sen [[dinlenme|istirahat|]] ve [[nefes alma/mola|teneff\xfcs|]] vaktini, ruhun rahat\u0131na, kalbin [[nefes almas\u0131na|teneff\xfcs\xfcne|]] [[sebep olan/vesile olan|medar olan|]] namaza [[harcasan|sarf etsen|]] o vakit, bereketli [[d\xfcnya r\u0131zk\u0131/ge\xe7imi|nafaka-i d\xfcnyeviye|]] ile beraber, senin [[ahiret r\u0131zk\u0131na/az\u0131\u011f\u0131na|nafaka-i uhreviyene|]] ve [[ahiret az\u0131\u011f\u0131na|z\xe2d-\u0131 \xe2hiretine|]] [[\xf6nemli|ehemmiyetli|]] bir [[kaynak|menba|]] olan, iki [[manevi maden/kaynak|maden-i manev\xee|]] bulursun:\\n\\nBirinci maden: B\xfct\xfcn ba\u011f\u0131ndaki (H\xe2\u015fiye[1]) yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fin \u2013\xe7i\xe7ekli olsun, meyveli olsun\u2013 her [[bitkinin|nebat\u0131n|]], her a\u011fac\u0131n [[Allah\'\u0131 anmalar\u0131ndan/zikirlerinden|tesbihat\u0131ndan|]], g\xfczel bir niyet ile bir [[pay|hisse|]] al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\n\u0130kinci maden: Hem bu ba\u011fdan \xe7\u0131kan [[\xfcr\xfcnlerden|mahsulattan|]] kim yese \u2013hayvan olsun, insan olsun; inek olsun, sinek olsun; m\xfc\u015fteri olsun, h\u0131rs\u0131z olsun\u2013 sana bir sadaka [[yerine ge\xe7er/say\u0131l\u0131r|h\xfckm\xfcne ge\xe7er|]]. Fakat o \u015fart ile ki sen, [[Ger\xe7ek r\u0131z\u0131k verici (Allah)|Rezzak-\u0131 Hakiki|]] [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] ve izni dairesinde [[kullansan/harcasan|tasarruf etsen|]] ve onun mal\u0131n\u0131, onun [[yaratt\u0131klar\u0131na|mahlukat\u0131na|]] veren bir [[da\u011f\u0131t\u0131m memuru|tevziat memuru|]] [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla/g\xf6z\xfcyle|nazar\u0131yla|]] kendine baksan\u2026\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bak, namaz\u0131 [[b\u0131rakan|terk eden|]] ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[zarar eder|hasaret eder|]], ne kadar [[\xf6nemli|ehemmiyetli|]] bir serveti kaybeder ve [[\xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya|sa\u2019ye|]] pek b\xfcy\xfck bir [[istek/arzu|\u015fevk|]] veren ve [[i\u015fte/eylemde|amelde|]] b\xfcy\xfck bir [[manevi g\xfc\xe7|kuvve-i manev\xee|]] [[sa\u011flayan|temin eden|]] o iki neticeden ve o iki madenden mahrum kal\u0131r, [[batr/t\xfckenir|iflas eder|]]. Hatt\xe2 ihtiyarland\u0131k\xe7a bah\xe7ecilikten usan\u0131r, [[bezginlik gelir/gev\u015feklik gelir|f\xfctur gelir|]]. \u201cNeme l\xe2z\u0131m.\u201d der. \u201cBen zaten d\xfcnyadan gidiyorum. Bu kadar zahmeti ne i\xe7in \xe7ekece\u011fim?\u201d diyecek, kendini tembelli\u011fe atacak. Fakat [[\xf6nceki|evvelki|]] adam der: \u201cDaha [[fazla/\xe7ok|ziyade|]] ibadetle beraber [[helal \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya|sa\u2019y-i hel\xe2le|]] \xe7al\u0131\u015faca\u011f\u0131m. T\xe2 kabrime daha [[fazla|ziyade|]] \u0131\u015f\u0131k g\xf6nderece\u011fim, \xe2hiretime daha [[fazla|ziyade|]] [[az\u0131k/erzak|zah\xeere|]] [[elde edece\u011fim/sa\u011flayaca\u011f\u0131m|tedarik edece\u011fim|]].\u201d\\n\\n[[K\u0131saca/\xd6zetle|Elhas\u0131l|]]: Ey nefis! Bil ki d\xfcnk\xfc g\xfcn senin elinden \xe7\u0131kt\u0131. Yar\u0131n ise senin elinde senet yok ki ona [[sahipsin|m\xe2liksin|]]. \xd6yle ise [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] \xf6mr\xfcn\xfc, bulundu\u011fun g\xfcn bil. [[En az\u0131ndan/Hi\xe7 olmazsa|L\xe2ekall|]] g\xfcn\xfcn bir saatini, [[yedek ak\xe7e/zor zaman paras\u0131|ihtiyat ak\xe7esi|]] gibi [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] [[gelecek (ahiret)|istikbal|]] i\xe7in [[olu\u015fturulan/kurulan|te\u015fkil olunan|]] bir [[ahiret sand\u0131\u011f\u0131/kutusu|sanduk\xe7a-i uhreviye|]] olan bir mescide veya bir seccadeye at.\\n\\nHem bil ki her yeni g\xfcn, sana hem herkese, bir yeni \xe2lemin kap\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r. E\u011fer namaz k\u0131lmazsan senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemin [[karanl\u0131kl\u0131|zul\xfcmatl\u0131|]] ve peri\u015fan bir halde gider, senin [[zarar\u0131na/kar\u015f\u0131t olarak|aleyhinde|]] [[misal aleminde/g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcler d\xfcnyas\u0131nda|\xe2lem-i misalde|]] [[\u015fahitlik eder|\u015fehadet eder|]]. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] herkesin, her g\xfcnde, \u015fu \xe2lemden bir [[\xf6zel/kendine has|mahsus|]] \xe2lemi var. Hem o \xe2lemin [[niteli\u011fi/durumu|keyfiyeti|]], o adam\u0131n kalbine ve ameline [[ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r|tabidir|]]. Nas\u0131l ki [[aynanda|\xe2yinende|]] g\xf6r\xfcnen muhte\u015fem bir saray, \xe2yinenin rengine bakar. Siyah ise siyah g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 ise k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. Hem onun [[niteli\u011fine/durumuna|keyfiyetine|]] bakar. O \xe2yine \u015fi\u015fesi d\xfczg\xfcn ise saray\u0131 g\xfczel g\xf6sterir. D\xfczg\xfcn de\u011fil ise \xe7irkin g\xf6sterir. En nazik \u015feyleri kaba g\xf6sterdi\u011fi [[gibi/benzeri|misill\xfc|]] sen kalbinle, akl\u0131nla, amelinle, g\xf6nl\xfcnle, kendi \xe2leminin \u015feklini de\u011fi\u015ftirirsin. Ya [[zarar\u0131na|aleyhinde|]] ya [[yarar\u0131na|lehinde|]] [[\u015fahitlik ettirebilirsin|\u015fehadet ettirebilirsin|]].\\n\\nE\u011fer namaz\u0131 k\u0131lsan o namaz\u0131n ile o \xe2lemin [[Celal sahibi Sanatk\xe2r\u0131na (Allah\'a)|S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019ine|]] [[y\xf6nelsen|m\xfcteveccih olsan|]] birden, sana bakan \xe2lemin [[ayd\u0131nlan\u0131r/nurlan\u0131r|tenevv\xfcr eder|]]. \xc2deta namaz\u0131n bir elektrik lambas\u0131 ve namaza niyetin, onun d\xfc\u011fmesine dokunmas\u0131 gibi o \xe2lemin [[karanl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131|zul\xfcmat\u0131n\u0131|]] da\u011f\u0131t\u0131r ve o [[d\xfcnyan\u0131n karga\u015fas\u0131ndaki/kar\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndaki|herc \xfc merc-i d\xfcnyeviyedeki|]] karmakar\u0131\u015f\u0131k [[peri\u015fanl\u0131k/da\u0131n\u0131kl\u0131k|peri\u015faniyet|]] i\xe7indeki [[de\u011fi\u015fimler/ba\u015fkala\u015fmalar|tebedd\xfclat|]] ve [[hareketler|harek\xe2t|]], hikmetli bir [[d\xfczen|intizam|]] ve manidar bir [[kudret yaz\u0131s\u0131|kitabet-i kudret|]] oldu\u011funu g\xf6sterir. [[Allah g\xf6klerin ve yerin nurudur.|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f \u0646\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|Nur Suresi, 35. Ayet]] [[nurlarla dolu ayetinden|\xe2yet-i p\xfcr-envar\u0131ndan|]] bir nuru, senin kalbine serper. Senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemini, o nurun [[yans\u0131mas\u0131yla|in\u2019ikas\u0131yla|]] \u0131\u015f\u0131kland\u0131r\u0131r. Senin [[yarar\u0131na|lehinde|]] [[nurlulukla/ayd\u0131nl\u0131kla|nuraniyetle|]] [[\u015fahitlik ettirir|\u015fehadet ettirir|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:34","oldText":"\xd6yle ise ben de sana derim ki: E\u011fer y\xfcz kuru\u015f bir g\xfcndelik ile \xe7al\u0131\u015fsan sonra biri gelse, dese ki: \u201cGel on dakika kadar \u015furay\u0131 kaz, y\xfcz lira [[k\u0131ymetinde|de\u011ferinde]] bir p\u0131rlanta ve bir z\xfcmr\xfct bulacaks\u0131n.\u201d Sen ona: \u201cYok, gelmem. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc on kuru\u015f g\xfcndeli\u011fimden kesilecek, [[nafakam|ge\xe7im param/yiyecek param]] azalacak.\u201d desen, ne kadar [[divanece|delice/ak\u0131ls\u0131zca]] bir bahane oldu\u011funu elbette bilirsin.\\n\\nAynen onun gibi sen \u015fu ba\u011f\u0131nda, [[nafakan|ge\xe7imin/yiyece\u011fin]] i\xe7in i\u015fliyorsun. E\u011fer farz namaz\u0131 [[terk etsen|b\u0131raksan/terk etsen]] b\xfct\xfcn [[sa\u2019yin|\xe7al\u0131\u015fman\u0131n/eme\u011fin]] [[semeresi|meyvesi/sonucu]], yaln\u0131z [[d\xfcnyev\xee|d\xfcnyaya ait]] ve [[ehemmiyetsiz|\xf6nemsiz]] ve bereketsiz bir [[nafakaya|ge\xe7imli\u011fe/r\u0131zka]] [[m\xfcnhas\u0131r kal\u0131r|s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 kal\u0131r/\xf6zg\xfc kal\u0131r]]. E\u011fer sen [[istirahat|dinlenme]] ve [[teneff\xfcs|nefes alma/mola]] vaktini, ruhun rahat\u0131na, kalbin [[teneff\xfcs\xfcne|nefes almas\u0131na]] [[medar olan|sebep olan/vesile olan]] namaza [[sarf etsen|harcasan]] o vakit, bereketli [[nafaka-i d\xfcnyeviye|d\xfcnya r\u0131zk\u0131/ge\xe7imi]] ile beraber, senin [[nafaka-i uhreviyene|ahiret r\u0131zk\u0131na/az\u0131\u011f\u0131na]] ve [[z\xe2d-\u0131 \xe2hiretine|ahiret az\u0131\u011f\u0131na]] [[ehemmiyetli|\xf6nemli]] bir [[menba|kaynak]] olan, iki [[maden-i manev\xee|manevi maden/kaynak]] bulursun:\\n\\nBirinci maden: B\xfct\xfcn ba\u011f\u0131ndaki (H\xe2\u015fiye[1]) yeti\u015ftirdi\u011fin \u2013\xe7i\xe7ekli olsun, meyveli olsun\u2013 her [[nebat\u0131n|bitkinin]], her a\u011fac\u0131n [[tesbihat\u0131ndan|Allah\'\u0131 anmalar\u0131ndan/zikirlerinden]], g\xfczel bir niyet ile bir [[hisse|pay]] al\u0131yorsun.\\n\\n\u0130kinci maden: Hem bu ba\u011fdan \xe7\u0131kan [[mahsulattan|\xfcr\xfcnlerden]] kim yese \u2013hayvan olsun, insan olsun; inek olsun, sinek olsun; m\xfc\u015fteri olsun, h\u0131rs\u0131z olsun\u2013 sana bir sadaka [[h\xfckm\xfcne ge\xe7er|yerine ge\xe7er/say\u0131l\u0131r]]. Fakat o \u015fart ile ki sen, [[Rezzak-\u0131 Hakiki|Ger\xe7ek r\u0131z\u0131k verici (Allah)]] [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] ve izni dairesinde [[tasarruf etsen|kullansan/harcasan]] ve onun mal\u0131n\u0131, onun [[mahlukat\u0131na|yaratt\u0131klar\u0131na]] veren bir [[tevziat memuru|da\u011f\u0131t\u0131m memuru]] [[nazar\u0131yla|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla/g\xf6z\xfcyle]] kendine baksan\u2026\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bak, namaz\u0131 [[terk eden|b\u0131rakan]] ne kadar b\xfcy\xfck bir [[hasaret eder|zarar eder]], ne kadar [[ehemmiyetli|\xf6nemli]] bir serveti kaybeder ve [[sa\u2019ye|\xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya]] pek b\xfcy\xfck bir [[\u015fevk|istek/arzu]] veren ve [[amelde|i\u015fte/eylemde]] b\xfcy\xfck bir [[kuvve-i manev\xee|manevi g\xfc\xe7]] [[temin eden|sa\u011flayan]] o iki neticeden ve o iki madenden mahrum kal\u0131r, [[iflas eder|batr/t\xfckenir]]. Hatt\xe2 ihtiyarland\u0131k\xe7a bah\xe7ecilikten usan\u0131r, [[f\xfctur gelir|bezginlik gelir/gev\u015feklik gelir]]. \u201cNeme l\xe2z\u0131m.\u201d der. \u201cBen zaten d\xfcnyadan gidiyorum. Bu kadar zahmeti ne i\xe7in \xe7ekece\u011fim?\u201d diyecek, kendini tembelli\u011fe atacak. Fakat [[evvelki|\xf6nceki]] adam der: \u201cDaha [[ziyade|fazla/\xe7ok]] ibadetle beraber [[sa\u2019y-i hel\xe2le|helal \xe7al\u0131\u015fmaya]] \xe7al\u0131\u015faca\u011f\u0131m. T\xe2 kabrime daha [[ziyade|fazla]] \u0131\u015f\u0131k g\xf6nderece\u011fim, \xe2hiretime daha [[ziyade|fazla]] [[zah\xeere|az\u0131k/erzak]] [[tedarik edece\u011fim|elde edece\u011fim/sa\u011flayaca\u011f\u0131m]].\u201d\\n\\n[[Elhas\u0131l|K\u0131saca/\xd6zetle]]: Ey nefis! Bil ki d\xfcnk\xfc g\xfcn senin elinden \xe7\u0131kt\u0131. Yar\u0131n ise senin elinde senet yok ki ona [[m\xe2liksin|sahipsin]]. \xd6yle ise [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] \xf6mr\xfcn\xfc, bulundu\u011fun g\xfcn bil. [[L\xe2ekall|En az\u0131ndan/Hi\xe7 olmazsa]] g\xfcn\xfcn bir saatini, [[ihtiyat ak\xe7esi|yedek ak\xe7e/zor zaman paras\u0131]] gibi [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] [[istikbal|gelecek (ahiret)]] i\xe7in [[te\u015fkil olunan|olu\u015fturulan/kurulan]] bir [[sanduk\xe7a-i uhreviye|ahiret sand\u0131\u011f\u0131/kutusu]] olan bir mescide veya bir seccadeye at.\\n\\nHem bil ki her yeni g\xfcn, sana hem herkese, bir yeni \xe2lemin kap\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r. E\u011fer namaz k\u0131lmazsan senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemin [[zul\xfcmatl\u0131|karanl\u0131kl\u0131]] ve peri\u015fan bir halde gider, senin [[aleyhinde|zarar\u0131na/kar\u015f\u0131t olarak]] [[\xe2lem-i misalde|misal aleminde/g\xf6r\xfcnt\xfcler d\xfcnyas\u0131nda]] [[\u015fehadet eder|\u015fahitlik eder]]. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] herkesin, her g\xfcnde, \u015fu \xe2lemden bir [[mahsus|\xf6zel/kendine has]] \xe2lemi var. Hem o \xe2lemin [[keyfiyeti|niteli\u011fi/durumu]], o adam\u0131n kalbine ve ameline [[tabidir|ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r]]. Nas\u0131l ki [[\xe2yinende|aynanda]] g\xf6r\xfcnen muhte\u015fem bir saray, \xe2yinenin rengine bakar. Siyah ise siyah g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 ise k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcr. Hem onun [[keyfiyetine|niteli\u011fine/durumuna]] bakar. O \xe2yine \u015fi\u015fesi d\xfczg\xfcn ise saray\u0131 g\xfczel g\xf6sterir. D\xfczg\xfcn de\u011fil ise \xe7irkin g\xf6sterir. En nazik \u015feyleri kaba g\xf6sterdi\u011fi [[misill\xfc|gibi/benzeri]] sen kalbinle, akl\u0131nla, amelinle, g\xf6nl\xfcnle, kendi \xe2leminin \u015feklini de\u011fi\u015ftirirsin. Ya [[aleyhinde|zarar\u0131na]] ya [[lehinde|yarar\u0131na]] [[\u015fehadet ettirebilirsin|\u015fahitlik ettirebilirsin]].\\n\\nE\u011fer namaz\u0131 k\u0131lsan o namaz\u0131n ile o \xe2lemin [[S\xe2ni\u2019-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019ine|Celal sahibi Sanatk\xe2r\u0131na (Allah\'a)]] [[m\xfcteveccih olsan|y\xf6nelsen]] birden, sana bakan \xe2lemin [[tenevv\xfcr eder|ayd\u0131nlan\u0131r/nurlan\u0131r]]. \xc2deta namaz\u0131n bir elektrik lambas\u0131 ve namaza niyetin, onun d\xfc\u011fmesine dokunmas\u0131 gibi o \xe2lemin [[zul\xfcmat\u0131n\u0131|karanl\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131]] da\u011f\u0131t\u0131r ve o [[herc \xfc merc-i d\xfcnyeviyedeki|d\xfcnyan\u0131n karga\u015fas\u0131ndaki/kar\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndaki]] karmakar\u0131\u015f\u0131k [[peri\u015faniyet|peri\u015fanl\u0131k/da\u0131n\u0131kl\u0131k]] i\xe7indeki [[tebedd\xfclat|de\u011fi\u015fimler/ba\u015fkala\u015fmalar]] ve [[harek\xe2t|hareketler]], hikmetli bir [[intizam|d\xfczen]] ve manidar bir [[kitabet-i kudret|kudret yaz\u0131s\u0131]] oldu\u011funu g\xf6sterir. [[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f \u0646\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0670\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0636\u0650|Allah g\xf6klerin ve yerin nurudur.|Nur Suresi, 35. Ayet]] [[\xe2yet-i p\xfcr-envar\u0131ndan|nurlarla dolu ayetinden]] bir nuru, senin kalbine serper. Senin o g\xfcnk\xfc \xe2lemini, o nurun [[in\u2019ikas\u0131yla|yans\u0131mas\u0131yla]] \u0131\u015f\u0131kland\u0131r\u0131r. Senin [[lehinde|yarar\u0131na]] [[nuraniyetle|nurlulukla/ayd\u0131nl\u0131kla]] [[\u015fehadet ettirir|\u015fahitlik ettirir]]."},{"pageId":4,"rawText":"Sak\u0131n deme: \u201cBenim namaz\u0131m nerede, \u015fu hakikat-i namaz nerede?\u201d Zira bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011fi, bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131 gibi kendi a\u011fac\u0131n\u0131 tavsif eder. Fark yaln\u0131z icmal ve tafsil ile oldu\u011fu gibi; senin ve benim gibi bir \xe2m\xeenin \u2013velev hissetmezse\u2013 namaz\u0131, b\xfcy\xfck bir velinin namaz\u0131 gibi \u015fu nurdan bir hissesi var, \u015fu hakikatten bir s\u0131rr\u0131 vard\u0131r, velev \u015fuurun taalluk etmezse. Fakat derecata g\xf6re inki\u015faf ve tenevv\xfcr\xfc ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131d\u0131r. Nas\u0131l bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011finden, t\xe2 m\xfckemmel bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131na kadar ne kadar meratib bulunur. \xd6yle de namaz\u0131n derecat\u0131nda da daha fazla meratib bulunabilir. Fakat b\xfct\xfcn o meratibde, o hakikat-i nuraniyenin esas\u0131 bulunur.\\n\\n\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0645\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \xab\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650\xbb \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0627\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e\\n\\n***\\n\\nYirmi Birinci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn \u0130kinci Makam\u0131\\n\\nKalbin be\u015f yaras\u0131na be\u015f merhemi tazammun eder.\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0636\u064f\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650\\n\\nEy maraz-\u0131 vesvese ile m\xfcptela! Biliyor musun vesvesen neye benzer? Musibete benzer. Ehemmiyet verdik\xe7e \u015fi\u015fer, ehemmiyet vermezsen s\xf6ner. Ona b\xfcy\xfck nazar\u0131yla baksan b\xfcy\xfcr. K\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6rsen k\xfc\xe7\xfcl\xfcr. Korksan a\u011f\u0131rla\u015f\u0131r, hasta eder. Havf etmezsen hafif olur, mahf\xee kal\u0131r. Mahiyetini bilmezsen devam eder, yerle\u015fir. Mahiyetini bilsen, onu tan\u0131san gider. \xd6yle ise \u015fu musibetli vesvesenin aksam-\u0131 kes\xeeresinden kes\xeer\xfc\u2019l-vuku olan yaln\u0131z be\u015f vechini beyan edece\u011fim. Belki sana ve bana \u015fifa olur. Zira \u015fu vesvese \xf6yle bir \u015feydir ki cehil onu davet eder, ilim onu tard eder. Tan\u0131mazsan gelir, tan\u0131san gider.\\n\\nBirinci Vecih\\n\\nBirinci yara, \u015feytan evvela \u015f\xfcpheyi kalbe atar. E\u011fer kalp kabul etmezse \u015f\xfcpheden \u015fetme d\xf6ner. Hayale kar\u015f\u0131 \u015fetme benzer baz\u0131 pis hat\u0131ralar\u0131 ve m\xfcnaf\xee-i edep \xe7irkin halleri tasvir eder. Kalbe \u201cEyvah!\u201d dedirtir, yeise d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. Vesveseli adam zanneder ki kalbi, Rabb\u2019ine kar\u015f\u0131 s\xfb-i edepte bulunuyor. M\xfcthi\u015f bir halecan ve heyecan hisseder. Bundan kurtulmak i\xe7in huzurdan ka\xe7ar, gaflete dalmak ister.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi budur:\\n\\nBak ey b\xee\xe7are vesveseli adam! Tela\u015f etme. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin hat\u0131r\u0131na gelen \u015fetim de\u011fil belki tahayy\xfcld\xfcr. Tahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr, k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi tahayy\xfcl-\xfc \u015fetim dahi \u015fetim de\u011fildir. Zira mant\u0131k\xe7a tahayy\xfcl, h\xfck\xfcm de\u011fildir. \u015eetim ise h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Hem bununla beraber o \xe7irkin s\xf6zler, senin kalbinin s\xf6zleri de\u011fil. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin kalbin ondan m\xfcteessir ve m\xfcteessiftir. Belki kalbe yak\u0131n olan l\xfcmme-i \u015feytan\xeeden geliyor. Vesvesenin zarar\u0131, tevehh\xfcm-\xfc zarard\u0131r. Yani onu zararl\u0131 tevehh\xfcm etmekle kalben mutazarr\u0131r olmakt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc h\xfck\xfcms\xfcz bir tahayy\xfcl\xfc hakikat tevehh\xfcm eder. Hem \u015feytan\u0131n i\u015fini kendi kalbine mal eder. Onun s\xf6z\xfcn\xfc, ondan zanneder. Zarar anlar, zarara d\xfc\u015fer. Zaten \u015feytan\u0131n da istedi\u011fi odur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci Vecih\\n\\nBudur ki: Manalar kalpten \xe7\u0131kt\u0131klar\u0131 vakit, suretlerden \xe7\u0131plak olarak hayale girerler, oradan suretleri giyerler. Hayal ise her vakit bir sebep taht\u0131nda bir nevi suretleri nesceder. Ehemmiyet verdi\u011fi \u015feyin suretlerini yol \xfcst\xfcnde b\u0131rak\u0131r. Hangi mana ge\xe7se ya ona giydirir ya takar ya bula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ya perde eder. E\u011fer manalar m\xfcnezzeh ve temiz iseler, suretler m\xfclevves ve rezil ise giymek yoktur fakat temas var. Vesveseli adam, temas\u0131 telebb\xfcsle iltibas eder. \u201cEyvah!\u201d der. \u201cKalbim ne kadar bozulmu\u015f. Bu sefillik, bu h\u0131sset-i nefis, beni matrud eder.\u201d \u015eeytan onun \u015fu damar\u0131ndan \xe7ok istifade eder.\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur:","modernText":"Sak\u0131n deme: \u201cBenim namaz\u0131m nerede, \u015fu [[namaz\u0131n hakikati/\xf6z\xfc|hakikat-i namaz|]] nerede?\u201d [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011fi, bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131 gibi kendi a\u011fac\u0131n\u0131 [[nitelendirir/tan\u0131mlar|tavsif eder|]]. Fark yaln\u0131z [[\xf6zet/k\u0131sa|icmal|]] ve [[ayr\u0131nt\u0131/detay|tafsil|]] ile oldu\u011fu gibi; senin ve benim gibi bir [[s\u0131radan insan\u0131n/avamdan birinin|\xe2m\xeenin|]] \u2013[[isterse/olsa bile|velev|]] hissetmezse\u2013 namaz\u0131, b\xfcy\xfck bir [[Allah dostunun|velinin|]] namaz\u0131 gibi \u015fu nurdan bir [[pay\u0131|hissesi|]] var, \u015fu hakikatten bir s\u0131rr\u0131 vard\u0131r, [[isterse|velev|]] [[bilincin|\u015fuurun|]] [[ilgilenmezse/kavramazsa|taalluk etmezse|]]. Fakat [[derecelere|derecata|]] g\xf6re [[a\xe7\u0131lma/geli\u015fme|inki\u015faf|]] ve [[nurlanmas\u0131/ayd\u0131nlanmas\u0131|tenevv\xfcr\xfc|]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131d\u0131r. Nas\u0131l bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011finden, t\xe2 m\xfckemmel bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131na kadar ne kadar [[mertebeler/dereceler|meratib|]] bulunur. \xd6yle de namaz\u0131n [[derecelerinde|derecat\u0131nda|]] da daha fazla [[mertebeler|meratib|]] bulunabilir. Fakat b\xfct\xfcn o [[mertebelerde|meratibde|]], o [[nurlu hakikatin|hakikat-i nuraniyenin|]] esas\u0131 bulunur.\\n\\n[[Allah\'\u0131m! \'Namaz dinin dire\u011fidir\' buyuran zata (Hz. Muhammed\'e), \xe2line ve b\xfct\xfcn ashab\u0131na sal\xe2t ve sel\xe2m eyle.|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651\u0645\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \xab\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650\xbb \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0627\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|]]\\n\\n***\\n\\nYirmi Birinci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn \u0130kinci Makam\u0131\\n\\nKalbin be\u015f yaras\u0131na be\u015f merhemi [[i\xe7erir/kapsar|tazammun eder|]].\\n\\n[[Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|]]\\n\\n[[Rabbim! \u015eeytanlar\u0131n k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtmalar\u0131ndan sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m! Ve Rabbim, yan\u0131mda bulunmalar\u0131ndan da sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m.|\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0636\u064f\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650|M\xfc\'min\xfbn Suresi, 97-98. Ayetler]]\\n\\nEy [[vesvese hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131|maraz-\u0131 vesvese|]] ile [[tutulmu\u015f/d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn|m\xfcptela|]]! Biliyor musun vesvesen neye benzer? [[Felakete/Belaya|Musibete|]] benzer. [[\xd6nem verdik\xe7e|Ehemmiyet verdik\xe7e|]] \u015fi\u015fer, [[\xf6nem vermezsen|ehemmiyet vermezsen|]] s\xf6ner. Ona b\xfcy\xfck [[g\xf6z\xfcyle/bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla|nazar\u0131yla|]] baksan b\xfcy\xfcr. K\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6rsen k\xfc\xe7\xfcl\xfcr. Korksan a\u011f\u0131rla\u015f\u0131r, hasta eder. [[Korkmazsan|Havf etmezsen|]] hafif olur, [[gizli|mahf\xee|]] kal\u0131r. [[\u0130\xe7 y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc/Niteli\u011fini|Mahiyetini|]] bilmezsen devam eder, yerle\u015fir. [[\u0130\xe7 y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc|Mahiyetini|]] bilsen, onu tan\u0131san gider. \xd6yle ise \u015fu [[belal\u0131/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131|musibetli|]] vesvesenin [[\xe7ok k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131ndan|aksam-\u0131 kes\xeeresinden|]] [[\xe7ok meydana gelen/s\u0131k g\xf6r\xfclen|kes\xeer\xfc\u2019l-vuku|]] yaln\u0131z be\u015f [[y\xf6n\xfcn\xfc/y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc|vechini|]] [[a\xe7\u0131klayaca\u011f\u0131m|beyan edece\u011fim|]]. [[Umulur ki|Belki|]] sana ve bana \u015fifa olur. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] \u015fu vesvese \xf6yle bir \u015feydir ki [[cahillik/bilgisizlik|cehil|]] onu davet eder, ilim onu [[kovar/uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r|tard eder|]]. Tan\u0131mazsan gelir, tan\u0131san gider.\\n\\nBirinci [[Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz|Vecih|]]\\n\\nBirinci yara, \u015feytan [[\xf6ncelikle|evvela|]] \u015f\xfcpheyi kalbe atar. E\u011fer kalp kabul etmezse \u015f\xfcpheden [[k\xfcfre/s\xf6vmeye|\u015fetme|]] d\xf6ner. Hayale kar\u015f\u0131 [[k\xfcfre|\u015fetme|]] benzer baz\u0131 pis hat\u0131ralar\u0131 ve [[edebe ayk\u0131r\u0131|m\xfcnaf\xee-i edep|]] \xe7irkin halleri [[resmeder/canland\u0131r\u0131r|tasvir eder|]]. Kalbe \u201cEyvah!\u201d dedirtir, [[\xfcmitsizli\u011fe|yeise|]] d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. Vesveseli adam zanneder ki kalbi, Rabb\u2019ine kar\u015f\u0131 [[edepsizlikte|s\xfb-i edepte|]] bulunuyor. M\xfcthi\u015f bir [[\xe7arp\u0131nt\u0131/heyecan|halecan|]] ve heyecan hisseder. Bundan kurtulmak i\xe7in huzurdan ka\xe7ar, gaflete dalmak ister.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi budur:\\n\\nBak ey [[\xe7aresiz/zavall\u0131|b\xee\xe7are|]] vesveseli adam! Tela\u015f etme. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin hat\u0131r\u0131na gelen [[s\xf6vme/k\xfcf\xfcr|\u015fetim|]] de\u011fil [[bilakis/aksine|belki|]] [[hayal etmedir|tahayy\xfcld\xfcr|]]. [[K\xfcfr\xfc hayal etmek|Tahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|]], k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[k\xfcfr\xfc/s\xf6vmeyi hayal etmek|tahayy\xfcl-\xfc \u015fetim|]] dahi [[s\xf6vme/k\xfcf\xfcr|\u015fetim|]] de\u011fildir. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] mant\u0131k\xe7a [[hayal etme|tahayy\xfcl|]], h\xfck\xfcm de\u011fildir. [[S\xf6vme/K\xfcf\xfcr|\u015eetim|]] ise h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Hem bununla beraber o \xe7irkin s\xf6zler, senin kalbinin s\xf6zleri de\u011fil. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin kalbin ondan [[etkilenmi\u015f/\xfcz\xfclm\xfc\u015f|m\xfcteessir|]] ve [[esef duymaktad\u0131r/\xfczg\xfcnd\xfcr|m\xfcteessiftir|]]. [[Bilakis/Aksine|Belki|]] kalbe yak\u0131n olan [[\u015feytan\u0131n vesvese verdi\u011fi noktadan|l\xfcmme-i \u015feytan\xeeden|]] geliyor. Vesvesenin zarar\u0131, [[zarar kuruntusudur/zarar zannetmektir|tevehh\xfcm-\xfc zarard\u0131r|]]. Yani onu zararl\u0131 [[zannetmekle/kuruntu yapmakla|tevehh\xfcm etmekle|]] [[kalp yoluyla|kalben|]] [[zarar g\xf6rmektir|mutazarr\u0131r olmakt\u0131r|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc h\xfck\xfcms\xfcz bir [[hayali|tahayy\xfcl\xfc|]] [[ger\xe7ek|hakikat|]] [[zanneder/kurar|tevehh\xfcm eder|]]. Hem \u015feytan\u0131n i\u015fini kendi kalbine mal eder. Onun s\xf6z\xfcn\xfc, ondan zanneder. Zarar anlar, zarara d\xfc\u015fer. Zaten \u015feytan\u0131n da istedi\u011fi odur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci [[Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz|Vecih|]]\\n\\nBudur ki: Manalar kalpten \xe7\u0131kt\u0131klar\u0131 vakit, suretlerden \xe7\u0131plak olarak hayale girerler, oradan suretleri giyerler. Hayal ise her vakit bir sebep [[alt\u0131nda|taht\u0131nda|]] bir [[\xe7e\u015fit|nevi|]] suretleri [[dokur/\xf6rer|nesceder|]]. [[\xd6nem verdi\u011fi|Ehemmiyet verdi\u011fi|]] \u015feyin suretlerini yol \xfcst\xfcnde b\u0131rak\u0131r. Hangi mana ge\xe7se ya ona giydirir ya takar ya bula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ya perde eder. E\u011fer manalar [[temiz/uzak|m\xfcnezzeh|]] ve temiz iseler, suretler [[kirli/pis|m\xfclevves|]] ve rezil ise giymek yoktur fakat temas var. Vesveseli adam, temas\u0131 [[giyinmekle/bula\u015fmakla|telebb\xfcsle|]] [[kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r|iltibas eder|]]. \u201cEyvah!\u201d der. \u201cKalbim ne kadar bozulmu\u015f. Bu sefillik, bu [[nefsin al\xe7akl\u0131\u011f\u0131|h\u0131sset-i nefis|]], beni [[kovulmu\u015f yapar/d\u0131\u015flanm\u0131\u015f k\u0131lar|matrud eder|]].\u201d \u015eeytan onun \u015fu damar\u0131ndan \xe7ok [[yararlan\u0131r|istifade eder|]].\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur:","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:36","oldText":"Sak\u0131n deme: \u201cBenim namaz\u0131m nerede, \u015fu [[hakikat-i namaz|namaz\u0131n hakikati/\xf6z\xfc]] nerede?\u201d [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011fi, bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131 gibi kendi a\u011fac\u0131n\u0131 [[tavsif eder|nitelendirir/tan\u0131mlar]]. Fark yaln\u0131z [[icmal|\xf6zet/k\u0131sa]] ve [[tafsil|ayr\u0131nt\u0131/detay]] ile oldu\u011fu gibi; senin ve benim gibi bir [[\xe2m\xeenin|s\u0131radan insan\u0131n/avamdan birinin]] \u2013[[velev|isterse/olsa bile]] hissetmezse\u2013 namaz\u0131, b\xfcy\xfck bir [[velinin|Allah dostunun]] namaz\u0131 gibi \u015fu nurdan bir [[hissesi|pay\u0131]] var, \u015fu hakikatten bir s\u0131rr\u0131 vard\u0131r, [[velev|isterse]] [[\u015fuurun|bilincin]] [[taalluk etmezse|ilgilenmezse/kavramazsa]]. Fakat [[derecata|derecelere]] g\xf6re [[inki\u015faf|a\xe7\u0131lma/geli\u015fme]] ve [[tenevv\xfcr\xfc|nurlanmas\u0131/ayd\u0131nlanmas\u0131]] ayr\u0131 ayr\u0131d\u0131r. Nas\u0131l bir hurma \xe7ekirde\u011finden, t\xe2 m\xfckemmel bir hurma a\u011fac\u0131na kadar ne kadar [[meratib|mertebeler/dereceler]] bulunur. \xd6yle de namaz\u0131n [[derecat\u0131nda|derecelerinde]] da daha fazla [[meratib|mertebeler]] bulunabilir. Fakat b\xfct\xfcn o [[meratibde|mertebelerde]], o [[hakikat-i nuraniyenin|nurlu hakikatin]] esas\u0131 bulunur.\\n\\n[[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651\u0645\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \xab\u0627\u064e\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650\xbb \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u0670\u0649 \u0627\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0656 \u0627\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0639\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e|Allah\'\u0131m! \'Namaz dinin dire\u011fidir\' buyuran zata (Hz. Muhammed\'e), \xe2line ve b\xfct\xfcn ashab\u0131na sal\xe2t ve sel\xe2m eyle.]]\\n\\n***\\n\\nYirmi Birinci S\xf6z\u2019\xfcn \u0130kinci Makam\u0131\\n\\nKalbin be\u015f yaras\u0131na be\u015f merhemi [[tazammun eder|i\xe7erir/kapsar]].\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahm\xe2n ve Rah\xeem olan Allah\'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[\u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0637\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \u06de \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651 \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0636\u064f\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650|Rabbim! \u015eeytanlar\u0131n k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtmalar\u0131ndan sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m! Ve Rabbim, yan\u0131mda bulunmalar\u0131ndan da sana s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m.|M\xfc\'min\xfbn Suresi, 97-98. Ayetler]]\\n\\nEy [[maraz-\u0131 vesvese|vesvese hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131]] ile [[m\xfcptela|tutulmu\u015f/d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn]]! Biliyor musun vesvesen neye benzer? [[Musibete|Felakete/Belaya]] benzer. [[Ehemmiyet verdik\xe7e|\xd6nem verdik\xe7e]] \u015fi\u015fer, [[ehemmiyet vermezsen|\xf6nem vermezsen]] s\xf6ner. Ona b\xfcy\xfck [[nazar\u0131yla|g\xf6z\xfcyle/bak\u0131\u015f\u0131yla]] baksan b\xfcy\xfcr. K\xfc\xe7\xfck g\xf6rsen k\xfc\xe7\xfcl\xfcr. Korksan a\u011f\u0131rla\u015f\u0131r, hasta eder. [[Havf etmezsen|Korkmazsan]] hafif olur, [[mahf\xee|gizli]] kal\u0131r. [[Mahiyetini|\u0130\xe7 y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc/Niteli\u011fini]] bilmezsen devam eder, yerle\u015fir. [[Mahiyetini|\u0130\xe7 y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc]] bilsen, onu tan\u0131san gider. \xd6yle ise \u015fu [[musibetli|belal\u0131/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131]] vesvesenin [[aksam-\u0131 kes\xeeresinden|\xe7ok k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131ndan]] [[kes\xeer\xfc\u2019l-vuku|\xe7ok meydana gelen/s\u0131k g\xf6r\xfclen]] yaln\u0131z be\u015f [[vechini|y\xf6n\xfcn\xfc/y\xfcz\xfcn\xfc]] [[beyan edece\u011fim|a\xe7\u0131klayaca\u011f\u0131m]]. [[Belki|Umulur ki]] sana ve bana \u015fifa olur. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] \u015fu vesvese \xf6yle bir \u015feydir ki [[cehil|cahillik/bilgisizlik]] onu davet eder, ilim onu [[tard eder|kovar/uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r]]. Tan\u0131mazsan gelir, tan\u0131san gider.\\n\\nBirinci [[Vecih|Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz]]\\n\\nBirinci yara, \u015feytan [[evvela|\xf6ncelikle]] \u015f\xfcpheyi kalbe atar. E\u011fer kalp kabul etmezse \u015f\xfcpheden [[\u015fetme|k\xfcfre/s\xf6vmeye]] d\xf6ner. Hayale kar\u015f\u0131 [[\u015fetme|k\xfcfre]] benzer baz\u0131 pis hat\u0131ralar\u0131 ve [[m\xfcnaf\xee-i edep|edebe ayk\u0131r\u0131]] \xe7irkin halleri [[tasvir eder|resmeder/canland\u0131r\u0131r]]. Kalbe \u201cEyvah!\u201d dedirtir, [[yeise|\xfcmitsizli\u011fe]] d\xfc\u015f\xfcrt\xfcr. Vesveseli adam zanneder ki kalbi, Rabb\u2019ine kar\u015f\u0131 [[s\xfb-i edepte|edepsizlikte]] bulunuyor. M\xfcthi\u015f bir [[halecan|\xe7arp\u0131nt\u0131/heyecan]] ve heyecan hisseder. Bundan kurtulmak i\xe7in huzurdan ka\xe7ar, gaflete dalmak ister.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi budur:\\n\\nBak ey [[b\xee\xe7are|\xe7aresiz/zavall\u0131]] vesveseli adam! Tela\u015f etme. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin hat\u0131r\u0131na gelen [[\u015fetim|s\xf6vme/k\xfcf\xfcr]] de\u011fil [[belki|bilakis/aksine]] [[tahayy\xfcld\xfcr|hayal etmedir]]. [[Tahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|K\xfcfr\xfc hayal etmek]], k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[tahayy\xfcl-\xfc \u015fetim|k\xfcfr\xfc/s\xf6vmeyi hayal etmek]] dahi [[\u015fetim|s\xf6vme/k\xfcf\xfcr]] de\u011fildir. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] mant\u0131k\xe7a [[tahayy\xfcl|hayal etme]], h\xfck\xfcm de\u011fildir. [[\u015eetim|S\xf6vme/K\xfcf\xfcr]] ise h\xfck\xfcmd\xfcr. Hem bununla beraber o \xe7irkin s\xf6zler, senin kalbinin s\xf6zleri de\u011fil. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc senin kalbin ondan [[m\xfcteessir|etkilenmi\u015f/\xfcz\xfclm\xfc\u015f]] ve [[m\xfcteessiftir|esef duymaktad\u0131r/\xfczg\xfcnd\xfcr]]. [[Belki|Bilakis/Aksine]] kalbe yak\u0131n olan [[l\xfcmme-i \u015feytan\xeeden|\u015feytan\u0131n vesvese verdi\u011fi noktadan]] geliyor. Vesvesenin zarar\u0131, [[tevehh\xfcm-\xfc zarard\u0131r|zarar kuruntusudur/zarar zannetmektir]]. Yani onu zararl\u0131 [[tevehh\xfcm etmekle|zannetmekle/kuruntu yapmakla]] [[kalben|kalp yoluyla]] [[mutazarr\u0131r olmakt\u0131r|zarar g\xf6rmektir]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc h\xfck\xfcms\xfcz bir [[tahayy\xfcl\xfc|hayali]] [[hakikat|ger\xe7ek]] [[tevehh\xfcm eder|zanneder/kurar]]. Hem \u015feytan\u0131n i\u015fini kendi kalbine mal eder. Onun s\xf6z\xfcn\xfc, ondan zanneder. Zarar anlar, zarara d\xfc\u015fer. Zaten \u015feytan\u0131n da istedi\u011fi odur.\\n\\n\u0130kinci [[Vecih|Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz]]\\n\\nBudur ki: Manalar kalpten \xe7\u0131kt\u0131klar\u0131 vakit, suretlerden \xe7\u0131plak olarak hayale girerler, oradan suretleri giyerler. Hayal ise her vakit bir sebep [[taht\u0131nda|alt\u0131nda]] bir [[nevi|\xe7e\u015fit]] suretleri [[nesceder|dokur/\xf6rer]]. [[Ehemmiyet verdi\u011fi|\xd6nem verdi\u011fi]] \u015feyin suretlerini yol \xfcst\xfcnde b\u0131rak\u0131r. Hangi mana ge\xe7se ya ona giydirir ya takar ya bula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r ya perde eder. E\u011fer manalar [[m\xfcnezzeh|temiz/uzak]] ve temiz iseler, suretler [[m\xfclevves|kirli/pis]] ve rezil ise giymek yoktur fakat temas var. Vesveseli adam, temas\u0131 [[telebb\xfcsle|giyinmekle/bula\u015fmakla]] [[iltibas eder|kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r]]. \u201cEyvah!\u201d der. \u201cKalbim ne kadar bozulmu\u015f. Bu sefillik, bu [[h\u0131sset-i nefis|nefsin al\xe7akl\u0131\u011f\u0131]], beni [[matrud eder|kovulmu\u015f yapar/d\u0131\u015flanm\u0131\u015f k\u0131lar]].\u201d \u015eeytan onun \u015fu damar\u0131ndan \xe7ok [[istifade eder|yararlan\u0131r]].\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur:"},{"pageId":5,"rawText":"Dinle ey b\xee\xe7are! Nas\u0131l ki senin namaz\u0131n edeb-i nezihanesinin vesilesi olan zahir\xee taharete, batn\u0131n\u0131n b\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki necaset ona tesir etmez ve bozmaz. \xd6yle de ma\xe2n\xee-i mukaddesenin suret-i m\xfclevveseye m\xfccavereti zarar etmez. Mesela, sen \xe2y\xe2t-\u0131 \u0130lahiyeyi tefekk\xfcr ediyorsun. Birden bir maraz, ya bir i\u015ftiha ya bevl gibi bir emr-i m\xfcheyyic \u015fiddetle senin hissine dokunuyor. Elbette senin hayalin, deva-i illet ve kaza-i h\xe2cetin levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6recek, bakacak, onlara m\xfcnasip s\xfcfl\xee suretleri nescedecek. Ve gelen manalar ortalar\u0131ndan ge\xe7ecekler. Ge\xe7eceklere ne beis vard\u0131r, ne televv\xfcs var ve ne zarar var ve ne hatar var. Yaln\u0131z hatar ise hasr-\u0131 nazard\u0131r, zann-\u0131 zarard\u0131r.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc Vecih\\n\\nBudur ki: E\u015fya mabeynlerinde, baz\u0131 m\xfcnasebat-\u0131 hafiye bulunur. Hatt\xe2 hi\xe7 \xfcmit etmedi\u011fin \u015feyler i\xe7inde m\xfcnasebet ipleri bulunur. Ya bizzat bulunur veya senin hayalin, me\u015fgul oldu\u011fu sanata g\xf6re o ipleri yapm\u0131\u015f, onlar\u0131 birbiriyle ba\u011flam\u0131\u015f. \u015eu s\u0131rr-\u0131 m\xfcnasebettendir ki bazen bir mukaddes \u015feyi g\xf6rmek, bir m\xfclevves \u015feyi hat\u0131ra getirir.\\n\\nFenn-i beyanda beyan olundu\u011fu gibi \u201cHari\xe7te uzakl\u0131k sebebi olan z\u0131ddiyet ise hayalde sebeb-i kurbiyettir.\u201d Yani iki z\u0131dd\u0131n suretlerinin cem\u2019ine vas\u0131ta, bir m\xfcnasebet-i hayaliyedir. Bu m\xfcnasebetle gelen tahattura, tedai-yi efk\xe2r tabir edilir. Mesela, sen namazda, m\xfcn\xe2catta, K\xe2be kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda, huzur-u \u0130lah\xeede iken \xe2y\xe2t\u0131 tefekk\xfcrde oldu\u011fun bir halde; \u015fu tedai-yi efk\xe2r, seni tutup en uzak malayaniyat-\u0131 rezileye sevk eder.\\n\\nSenin ba\u015f\u0131n, b\xf6yle bir tedai-yi efk\xe2ra m\xfcptela ise sak\u0131n tela\u015f etme. Belki intibaha geldi\u011fin anda, d\xf6n. \u201cAman ne kusur ettim!\u201d deyip tetkikle me\u015fgul olup durma. T\xe2 o zay\u0131f m\xfcnasebet, senin dikkatinle kuvvet peyda etmesin. Zira teess\xfcr g\xf6sterdik\xe7e, ehemmiyet verdik\xe7e, senin o zay\u0131f tahatturun melekeye d\xf6ner. Bir maraz-\u0131 hayal\xee olur. Korkma, maraz-\u0131 kalb\xee de\u011fil. \u015eu nevi tahattur ise galiben ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r. Hususan hassas asab\xeelerde daha galiptir. \u015eeytan, \u015fu nevi vesvesenin madenini \xe7ok i\u015flettirir. \u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\nTedai-yi efk\xe2r, galiben ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r. Onda mes\u2019uliyet yoktur. Hem tedaide, m\xfccaveret var; temas ve ihtilat yoktur. Onun i\xe7in efk\xe2r\u0131n keyfiyetleri, birbirine sirayet etmez, birbirine zarar vermez. Nas\u0131l ki \u015feytan ile melek-i ilham, kalp taraflar\u0131nda m\xfccaveretleri var ve f\xfcccar ve ebrar\u0131n karabetleri ve bir meskende durmalar\u0131, zarar vermez. \xd6yle de tedai-yi efk\xe2r s\xe2ikas\u0131yla istemedi\u011fin pis hayalat, gelip nezih efk\xe2r\u0131n i\xe7ine girse zarar vermez. Me\u011fer kasden olsa veya zarar zann\u0131yla onunla ziyade me\u015fgul olsa. Hem bazen kalp yoruluyor. Fikir, kendini e\u011flendirmek i\xe7in rastgele bir \u015feyle me\u015fgul olur. \u015eeytan f\u0131rsat bulur, pis \u015feyleri \xf6n\xfcne serpiyor, s\xfcr\xfcyor.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc Vecih\\n\\nAmelin en iyi suretini taharriden ne\u015f\u2019et eden bir vesvesedir ki takva zann\u0131yla te\u015fedd\xfcd ettik\xe7e hal ona \u015fiddetlenir. Hatt\xe2 bir dereceye var\u0131r ki o adam amelin daha evl\xe2s\u0131n\u0131 ararken harama d\xfc\u015fer. Bazen bir s\xfcnnetin aramas\u0131, bir v\xe2cibi terk ettiriyor. \u201cAcaba amelim sahih oldu mu?\u201d der, iade eder. Bu hal devam eder. Gayet yeise d\xfc\u015fer. \u015eeytan \u015fu halinden istifade eder, onu yaralar.\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n iki merhemi var:\\n\\nBirinci merhem: Bu gibi vesvese Ehl-i \u0130tizal\u2019e l\xe2y\u0131kt\u0131r. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc onlar derler: \u201cMedar-\u0131 teklif olan ef\u2019al ve e\u015fya, kendi zat\u0131nda, \xe2hiret itibar\u0131yla ya h\xfcsn\xfc var; sonra o h\xfcsne binaen emredilmi\u015f veya kubhu var; sonra ona binaen nehyedilmi\u015f. Demek e\u015fyada, \xe2hiret ve hakikat nokta-i nazar\u0131nda olan h\xfcs\xfcn ve kubuh zat\xeedir; emir ve nehy-i \u0130lah\xee ona tabidir.\u201d Bu mezhebe g\xf6re insan, her i\u015fledi\u011fi amelde \u015f\xf6yle bir vesvese gelir: \u201cAcaba amelim nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirdeki g\xfczel surette yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015f m\u0131d\u0131r?\u201d","modernText":"Dinle ey [[\xe7aresiz/zavall\u0131|b\xee\xe7are|]]! Nas\u0131l ki senin namaz\u0131n [[temiz edebinin|edeb-i nezihanesinin|]] [[arac\u0131/sebebi|vesilesi|]] olan [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fteki/d\u0131\u015ftaki|zahir\xee|]] [[temizli\u011fe|taharete|]], [[karn\u0131n\u0131n/i\xe7inin|batn\u0131n\u0131n|]] [[i\xe7indeki/gizli k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki|b\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki|]] [[pislik|necaset|]] ona [[etki etmez|tesir etmez|]] ve bozmaz. \xd6yle de [[kutsal manalar\u0131n|ma\xe2n\xee-i mukaddesenin|]] [[pis surete/kirli \u015fekle|suret-i m\xfclevveseye|]] [[kom\u015fulu\u011fu/yak\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131|m\xfccavereti|]] zarar etmez. Mesela, sen [[\u0130lahi ayetleri|\xe2y\xe2t-\u0131 \u0130lahiyeyi|]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcyorsun|tefekk\xfcr ediyorsun|]]. Birden bir [[hastal\u0131k|maraz|]], ya bir [[i\u015ftah/arzu|i\u015ftiha|]] ya [[idrar|bevl|]] gibi bir [[heyecanland\u0131ran/harekete ge\xe7iren durum|emr-i m\xfcheyyic|]] \u015fiddetle senin hissine dokunuyor. Elbette senin hayalin, [[hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131n ilac\u0131|deva-i illet|]] ve [[tuvalet ihtiyac\u0131n\u0131 gidermenin|kaza-i h\xe2cetin|]] [[gereklerini/malzemelerini|levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|]] g\xf6recek, bakacak, onlara [[uygun|m\xfcnasip|]] [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131/baya\u011f\u0131|s\xfcfl\xee|]] suretleri [[dokuyacak/\xfcretecek|nescedecek|]]. Ve gelen manalar ortalar\u0131ndan ge\xe7ecekler. Ge\xe7eceklere ne [[sak\u0131nca/zarar|beis|]] vard\u0131r, ne [[kirlenme/bula\u015fma|televv\xfcs|]] var ve ne zarar var ve ne [[tehlike|hatar|]] var. Yaln\u0131z [[tehlike|hatar|]] ise [[bak\u0131\u015f\u0131 s\u0131n\u0131rlamakt\u0131r/dikkati oraya toplamakt\u0131r|hasr-\u0131 nazard\u0131r|]], [[zarar zannetmektir|zann-\u0131 zarard\u0131r|]].\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz|Vecih|]]\\n\\nBudur ki: [[\u015eeyler/Varl\u0131klar|E\u015fya|]] [[aralar\u0131nda|mabeynlerinde|]], baz\u0131 [[gizli ili\u015fkiler/ba\u011flar|m\xfcnasebat-\u0131 hafiye|]] bulunur. Hatt\xe2 hi\xe7 \xfcmit etmedi\u011fin \u015feyler i\xe7inde [[ili\u015fki/ba\u011f|m\xfcnasebet|]] ipleri bulunur. Ya [[kendili\u011finden/do\u011frudan|bizzat|]] bulunur veya senin hayalin, me\u015fgul oldu\u011fu sanata g\xf6re o ipleri yapm\u0131\u015f, onlar\u0131 birbiriyle ba\u011flam\u0131\u015f. \u015eu [[ili\u015fki s\u0131rr\u0131ndand\u0131r|s\u0131rr-\u0131 m\xfcnasebettendir|]] ki bazen bir [[kutsal|mukaddes|]] \u015feyi g\xf6rmek, bir [[kirli/pis|m\xfclevves|]] \u015feyi hat\u0131ra getirir.\\n\\n[[Beyan ilminde/Edebiyat biliminde|Fenn-i beyanda|]] beyan olundu\u011fu gibi \u201c[[D\u0131\u015fta/Ger\xe7ekte|Hari\xe7te|]] uzakl\u0131k sebebi olan [[z\u0131tl\u0131k|z\u0131ddiyet|]] ise hayalde [[yak\u0131nl\u0131k sebebidir|sebeb-i kurbiyettir|]].\u201d Yani iki z\u0131dd\u0131n suretlerinin [[toplanmas\u0131na/birle\u015fmesine|cem\u2019ine|]] [[ara\xe7|vas\u0131ta|]], bir [[hayali ili\u015fki/ba\u011flant\u0131d\u0131r|m\xfcnasebet-i hayaliyedir|]]. Bu [[ili\u015fkiyle|m\xfcnasebetle|]] gelen [[hat\u0131rlamaya|tahattura|]], [[fikirlerin \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131|tedai-yi efk\xe2r|]] [[denir/adland\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r|tabir edilir|]]. Mesela, sen namazda, [[yalvar\u0131\u015fta/duada|m\xfcn\xe2catta|]], K\xe2be kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda, [[Allah\'\u0131n huzurunda|huzur-u \u0130lah\xeede|]] iken [[ayetleri|\xe2y\xe2t\u0131|]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmekte|tefekk\xfcrde|]] oldu\u011fun bir halde; \u015fu [[fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131|tedai-yi efk\xe2r|]], seni tutup en uzak [[rezil ve bo\u015f \u015feylere|malayaniyat-\u0131 rezileye|]] [[y\xf6nlendirir/g\xf6t\xfcr\xfcr|sevk eder|]].\\n\\nSenin ba\u015f\u0131n, b\xf6yle bir [[fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131na|tedai-yi efk\xe2ra|]] [[tutulmu\u015f/d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn|m\xfcptela|]] ise sak\u0131n tela\u015f etme. [[Aksine/Bilakis|Belki|]] [[uyan\u0131kl\u0131\u011fa/fark\u0131ndal\u0131\u011fa|intibaha|]] geldi\u011fin anda, d\xf6n. \u201cAman ne kusur ettim!\u201d deyip [[incelemekle/ara\u015ft\u0131rmakla|tetkikle|]] me\u015fgul olup durma. T\xe2 o zay\u0131f [[ili\u015fki/ba\u011f|m\xfcnasebet|]], senin dikkatinle [[kuvvet bulmas\u0131n/g\xfc\xe7lenmesin|kuvvet peyda etmesin|]]. [[\xc7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] [[\xfcz\xfcnt\xfc/etkilenme|teess\xfcr|]] g\xf6sterdik\xe7e, [[\xf6nem|ehemmiyet|]] verdik\xe7e, senin o zay\u0131f [[hat\u0131rlaman|tahatturun|]] [[al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131\u011fa/yetiye|melekeye|]] d\xf6ner. Bir [[hayali hastal\u0131k|maraz-\u0131 hayal\xee|]] olur. Korkma, [[kalp hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131|maraz-\u0131 kalb\xee|]] de\u011fil. \u015eu [[t\xfcr/\xe7e\u015fit|nevi|]] [[hat\u0131rlama|tahattur|]] ise [[\xe7o\u011funlukla|galiben|]] [[istemsizdir/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131d\u0131r|ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r|]]. [[\xd6zellikle|Hususan|]] hassas [[sinirlilerde|asab\xeelerde|]] daha [[bask\u0131nd\u0131r/yayg\u0131nd\u0131r|galiptir|]]. \u015eeytan, \u015fu [[t\xfcr|nevi|]] vesvesenin madenini \xe7ok i\u015flettirir. \u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[Fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131|Tedai-yi efk\xe2r|]], [[\xe7o\u011funlukla|galiben|]] [[istemsizdir|ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r|]]. Onda [[sorumluluk|mes\u2019uliyet|]] yoktur. Hem [[\xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131mda|tedaide|]], [[kom\u015fuluk/yan yana olma|m\xfccaveret|]] var; temas ve [[kar\u0131\u015fma|ihtilat|]] yoktur. Onun i\xe7in [[fikirlerin|efk\xe2r\u0131n|]] [[nitelikleri/\xf6zellikleri|keyfiyetleri|]], birbirine [[bula\u015fmaz/ge\xe7mez|sirayet etmez|]], birbirine zarar vermez. Nas\u0131l ki \u015feytan ile [[ilham mele\u011fi|melek-i ilham|]], kalp taraflar\u0131nda [[kom\u015fuluklar\u0131/yak\u0131nl\u0131klar\u0131|m\xfccaveretleri|]] var ve [[g\xfcnahk\xe2rlar|f\xfcccar|]] ve [[iyilerin|ebrar\u0131n|]] [[yak\u0131nl\u0131klar\u0131|karabetleri|]] ve bir meskende durmalar\u0131, zarar vermez. \xd6yle de [[fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131 d\xfcrt\xfcs\xfcyle/sebebiyle|tedai-yi efk\xe2r s\xe2ikas\u0131yla|]] istemedi\u011fin pis [[hayaller|hayalat|]], gelip [[temiz|nezih|]] [[fikirlerin|efk\xe2r\u0131n|]] i\xe7ine girse zarar vermez. [[Ancak/\u015eu \u015fartla ki|Me\u011fer|]] [[bilerek/isteyerek|kasden|]] olsa veya zarar zann\u0131yla onunla [[fazla|ziyade|]] me\u015fgul olsa. Hem bazen kalp yoruluyor. Fikir, kendini e\u011flendirmek i\xe7in rastgele bir \u015feyle me\u015fgul olur. \u015eeytan f\u0131rsat bulur, pis \u015feyleri \xf6n\xfcne serpiyor, s\xfcr\xfcyor.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc [[Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz|Vecih|]]\\n\\nAmelin en iyi suretini [[aramaktan/ara\u015ft\u0131rmaktan|taharriden|]] [[\xe7\u0131kan/kaynaklanan|ne\u015f\u2019et eden|]] bir vesvesedir ki takva zann\u0131yla [[\u015fiddetlendirdik\xe7e/zorla\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131k\xe7a|te\u015fedd\xfcd ettik\xe7e|]] hal ona \u015fiddetlenir. Hatt\xe2 bir dereceye var\u0131r ki o adam amelin daha [[iyisini/\xfcst\xfcn\xfcn\xfc|evl\xe2s\u0131n\u0131|]] ararken harama d\xfc\u015fer. Bazen bir s\xfcnnetin aramas\u0131, bir [[yap\u0131lmas\u0131 zorunlu olan\u0131|v\xe2cibi|]] [[b\u0131rakt\u0131r\u0131yor|terk ettiriyor|]]. \u201cAcaba amelim [[do\u011fru/ge\xe7erli|sahih|]] oldu mu?\u201d der, [[tekrar eder|iade eder|]]. Bu hal devam eder. Gayet [[\xfcmitsizli\u011fe|yeise|]] d\xfc\u015fer. \u015eeytan \u015fu halinden [[yararlan\u0131r|istifade eder|]], onu yaralar.\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n iki merhemi var:\\n\\nBirinci merhem: Bu gibi vesvese [[Mutezile mezhebine (kaderi inkar edenler)|Ehl-i \u0130tizal\u2019e|]] [[yara\u015f\u0131r/uygundur|l\xe2y\u0131kt\u0131r|]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc onlar derler: \u201c[[sorumluluk kayna\u011f\u0131|Medar-\u0131 teklif|]] olan [[fiiller|ef\u2019al|]] ve e\u015fya, kendi zat\u0131nda, \xe2hiret [[bak\u0131m\u0131ndan|itibar\u0131yla|]] ya [[g\xfczelli\u011fi|h\xfcsn\xfc|]] var; sonra o [[g\xfczelli\u011fe|h\xfcsne|]] [[dayanarak|binaen|]] emredilmi\u015f veya [[\xe7irkinli\u011fi|kubhu|]] var; sonra ona [[dayanarak|binaen|]] [[yasaklanm\u0131\u015f|nehyedilmi\u015f|]]. Demek e\u015fyada, \xe2hiret ve hakikat [[bak\u0131\u015f a\xe7\u0131s\u0131nda|nokta-i nazar\u0131nda|]] olan [[g\xfczellik|h\xfcs\xfcn|]] ve [[\xe7irkinlik|kubuh|]] [[\xf6z\xfcndedir/kendindendir|zat\xeedir|]]; emir ve [[\u0130lahi yasak|nehy-i \u0130lah\xee|]] ona [[uymaktad\u0131r|tabidir|]].\u201d Bu mezhebe g\xf6re insan, her i\u015fledi\u011fi amelde \u015f\xf6yle bir vesvese gelir: \u201cAcaba amelim [[i\u015fin asl\u0131ndaki/ger\xe7ekteki|nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirdeki|]] g\xfczel [[bi\xe7imde|surette|]] yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015f m\u0131d\u0131r?\u201d","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:44","oldText":"Dinle ey [[b\xee\xe7are|\xe7aresiz/zavall\u0131]]! Nas\u0131l ki senin namaz\u0131n [[edeb-i nezihanesinin|temiz edebinin]] [[vesilesi|arac\u0131/sebebi]] olan [[zahir\xee|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fteki/d\u0131\u015ftaki]] [[taharete|temizli\u011fe]], [[batn\u0131n\u0131n|karn\u0131n\u0131n/i\xe7inin]] [[b\xe2t\u0131n\u0131ndaki|i\xe7indeki/gizli k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki]] [[necaset|pislik]] ona [[tesir etmez|etki etmez]] ve bozmaz. \xd6yle de [[ma\xe2n\xee-i mukaddesenin|kutsal manalar\u0131n]] [[suret-i m\xfclevveseye|pis surete/kirli \u015fekle]] [[m\xfccavereti|kom\u015fulu\u011fu/yak\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] zarar etmez. Mesela, sen [[\xe2y\xe2t-\u0131 \u0130lahiyeyi|\u0130lahi ayetleri]] [[tefekk\xfcr ediyorsun|d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcyorsun]]. Birden bir [[maraz|hastal\u0131k]], ya bir [[i\u015ftiha|i\u015ftah/arzu]] ya [[bevl|idrar]] gibi bir [[emr-i m\xfcheyyic|heyecanland\u0131ran/harekete ge\xe7iren durum]] \u015fiddetle senin hissine dokunuyor. Elbette senin hayalin, [[deva-i illet|hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131n ilac\u0131]] ve [[kaza-i h\xe2cetin|tuvalet ihtiyac\u0131n\u0131 gidermenin]] [[levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|gereklerini/malzemelerini]] g\xf6recek, bakacak, onlara [[m\xfcnasip|uygun]] [[s\xfcfl\xee|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131/baya\u011f\u0131]] suretleri [[nescedecek|dokuyacak/\xfcretecek]]. Ve gelen manalar ortalar\u0131ndan ge\xe7ecekler. Ge\xe7eceklere ne [[beis|sak\u0131nca/zarar]] vard\u0131r, ne [[televv\xfcs|kirlenme/bula\u015fma]] var ve ne zarar var ve ne [[hatar|tehlike]] var. Yaln\u0131z [[hatar|tehlike]] ise [[hasr-\u0131 nazard\u0131r|bak\u0131\u015f\u0131 s\u0131n\u0131rlamakt\u0131r/dikkati oraya toplamakt\u0131r]], [[zann-\u0131 zarard\u0131r|zarar zannetmektir]].\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[Vecih|Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz]]\\n\\nBudur ki: [[E\u015fya|\u015eeyler/Varl\u0131klar]] [[mabeynlerinde|aralar\u0131nda]], baz\u0131 [[m\xfcnasebat-\u0131 hafiye|gizli ili\u015fkiler/ba\u011flar]] bulunur. Hatt\xe2 hi\xe7 \xfcmit etmedi\u011fin \u015feyler i\xe7inde [[m\xfcnasebet|ili\u015fki/ba\u011f]] ipleri bulunur. Ya [[bizzat|kendili\u011finden/do\u011frudan]] bulunur veya senin hayalin, me\u015fgul oldu\u011fu sanata g\xf6re o ipleri yapm\u0131\u015f, onlar\u0131 birbiriyle ba\u011flam\u0131\u015f. \u015eu [[s\u0131rr-\u0131 m\xfcnasebettendir|ili\u015fki s\u0131rr\u0131ndand\u0131r]] ki bazen bir [[mukaddes|kutsal]] \u015feyi g\xf6rmek, bir [[m\xfclevves|kirli/pis]] \u015feyi hat\u0131ra getirir.\\n\\n[[Fenn-i beyanda|Beyan ilminde/Edebiyat biliminde]] beyan olundu\u011fu gibi \u201c[[Hari\xe7te|D\u0131\u015fta/Ger\xe7ekte]] uzakl\u0131k sebebi olan [[z\u0131ddiyet|z\u0131tl\u0131k]] ise hayalde [[sebeb-i kurbiyettir|yak\u0131nl\u0131k sebebidir]].\u201d Yani iki z\u0131dd\u0131n suretlerinin [[cem\u2019ine|toplanmas\u0131na/birle\u015fmesine]] [[vas\u0131ta|ara\xe7]], bir [[m\xfcnasebet-i hayaliyedir|hayali ili\u015fki/ba\u011flant\u0131d\u0131r]]. Bu [[m\xfcnasebetle|ili\u015fkiyle]] gelen [[tahattura|hat\u0131rlamaya]], [[tedai-yi efk\xe2r|fikirlerin \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131]] [[tabir edilir|denir/adland\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r]]. Mesela, sen namazda, [[m\xfcn\xe2catta|yalvar\u0131\u015fta/duada]], K\xe2be kar\u015f\u0131s\u0131nda, [[huzur-u \u0130lah\xeede|Allah\'\u0131n huzurunda]] iken [[\xe2y\xe2t\u0131|ayetleri]] [[tefekk\xfcrde|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmekte]] oldu\u011fun bir halde; \u015fu [[tedai-yi efk\xe2r|fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131]], seni tutup en uzak [[malayaniyat-\u0131 rezileye|rezil ve bo\u015f \u015feylere]] [[sevk eder|y\xf6nlendirir/g\xf6t\xfcr\xfcr]].\\n\\nSenin ba\u015f\u0131n, b\xf6yle bir [[tedai-yi efk\xe2ra|fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131na]] [[m\xfcptela|tutulmu\u015f/d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn]] ise sak\u0131n tela\u015f etme. [[Belki|Aksine/Bilakis]] [[intibaha|uyan\u0131kl\u0131\u011fa/fark\u0131ndal\u0131\u011fa]] geldi\u011fin anda, d\xf6n. \u201cAman ne kusur ettim!\u201d deyip [[tetkikle|incelemekle/ara\u015ft\u0131rmakla]] me\u015fgul olup durma. T\xe2 o zay\u0131f [[m\xfcnasebet|ili\u015fki/ba\u011f]], senin dikkatinle [[kuvvet peyda etmesin|kuvvet bulmas\u0131n/g\xfc\xe7lenmesin]]. [[Zira|\xc7\xfcnk\xfc]] [[teess\xfcr|\xfcz\xfcnt\xfc/etkilenme]] g\xf6sterdik\xe7e, [[ehemmiyet|\xf6nem]] verdik\xe7e, senin o zay\u0131f [[tahatturun|hat\u0131rlaman]] [[melekeye|al\u0131\u015fkanl\u0131\u011fa/yetiye]] d\xf6ner. Bir [[maraz-\u0131 hayal\xee|hayali hastal\u0131k]] olur. Korkma, [[maraz-\u0131 kalb\xee|kalp hastal\u0131\u011f\u0131]] de\u011fil. \u015eu [[nevi|t\xfcr/\xe7e\u015fit]] [[tahattur|hat\u0131rlama]] ise [[galiben|\xe7o\u011funlukla]] [[ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r|istemsizdir/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131d\u0131r]]. [[Hususan|\xd6zellikle]] hassas [[asab\xeelerde|sinirlilerde]] daha [[galiptir|bask\u0131nd\u0131r/yayg\u0131nd\u0131r]]. \u015eeytan, \u015fu [[nevi|t\xfcr]] vesvesenin madenini \xe7ok i\u015flettirir. \u015eu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[Tedai-yi efk\xe2r|Fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131]], [[galiben|\xe7o\u011funlukla]] [[ihtiyars\u0131zd\u0131r|istemsizdir]]. Onda [[mes\u2019uliyet|sorumluluk]] yoktur. Hem [[tedaide|\xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131mda]], [[m\xfccaveret|kom\u015fuluk/yan yana olma]] var; temas ve [[ihtilat|kar\u0131\u015fma]] yoktur. Onun i\xe7in [[efk\xe2r\u0131n|fikirlerin]] [[keyfiyetleri|nitelikleri/\xf6zellikleri]], birbirine [[sirayet etmez|bula\u015fmaz/ge\xe7mez]], birbirine zarar vermez. Nas\u0131l ki \u015feytan ile [[melek-i ilham|ilham mele\u011fi]], kalp taraflar\u0131nda [[m\xfccaveretleri|kom\u015fuluklar\u0131/yak\u0131nl\u0131klar\u0131]] var ve [[f\xfcccar|g\xfcnahk\xe2rlar]] ve [[ebrar\u0131n|iyilerin]] [[karabetleri|yak\u0131nl\u0131klar\u0131]] ve bir meskende durmalar\u0131, zarar vermez. \xd6yle de [[tedai-yi efk\xe2r s\xe2ikas\u0131yla|fikir \xe7a\u011fr\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131 d\xfcrt\xfcs\xfcyle/sebebiyle]] istemedi\u011fin pis [[hayalat|hayaller]], gelip [[nezih|temiz]] [[efk\xe2r\u0131n|fikirlerin]] i\xe7ine girse zarar vermez. [[Me\u011fer|Ancak/\u015eu \u015fartla ki]] [[kasden|bilerek/isteyerek]] olsa veya zarar zann\u0131yla onunla [[ziyade|fazla]] me\u015fgul olsa. Hem bazen kalp yoruluyor. Fikir, kendini e\u011flendirmek i\xe7in rastgele bir \u015feyle me\u015fgul olur. \u015eeytan f\u0131rsat bulur, pis \u015feyleri \xf6n\xfcne serpiyor, s\xfcr\xfcyor.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc [[Vecih|Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz]]\\n\\nAmelin en iyi suretini [[taharriden|aramaktan/ara\u015ft\u0131rmaktan]] [[ne\u015f\u2019et eden|\xe7\u0131kan/kaynaklanan]] bir vesvesedir ki takva zann\u0131yla [[te\u015fedd\xfcd ettik\xe7e|\u015fiddetlendirdik\xe7e/zorla\u015ft\u0131rd\u0131k\xe7a]] hal ona \u015fiddetlenir. Hatt\xe2 bir dereceye var\u0131r ki o adam amelin daha [[evl\xe2s\u0131n\u0131|iyisini/\xfcst\xfcn\xfcn\xfc]] ararken harama d\xfc\u015fer. Bazen bir s\xfcnnetin aramas\u0131, bir [[v\xe2cibi|yap\u0131lmas\u0131 zorunlu olan\u0131]] [[terk ettiriyor|b\u0131rakt\u0131r\u0131yor]]. \u201cAcaba amelim [[sahih|do\u011fru/ge\xe7erli]] oldu mu?\u201d der, [[iade eder|tekrar eder]]. Bu hal devam eder. Gayet [[yeise|\xfcmitsizli\u011fe]] d\xfc\u015fer. \u015eeytan \u015fu halinden [[istifade eder|yararlan\u0131r]], onu yaralar.\\n\\n\u015eu yaran\u0131n iki merhemi var:\\n\\nBirinci merhem: Bu gibi vesvese [[Ehl-i \u0130tizal\u2019e|Mutezile mezhebine (kaderi inkar edenler)]] [[l\xe2y\u0131kt\u0131r|yara\u015f\u0131r/uygundur]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc onlar derler: \u201c[[Medar-\u0131 teklif|sorumluluk kayna\u011f\u0131]] olan [[ef\u2019al|fiiller]] ve e\u015fya, kendi zat\u0131nda, \xe2hiret [[itibar\u0131yla|bak\u0131m\u0131ndan]] ya [[h\xfcsn\xfc|g\xfczelli\u011fi]] var; sonra o [[h\xfcsne|g\xfczelli\u011fe]] [[binaen|dayanarak]] emredilmi\u015f veya [[kubhu|\xe7irkinli\u011fi]] var; sonra ona [[binaen|dayanarak]] [[nehyedilmi\u015f|yasaklanm\u0131\u015f]]. Demek e\u015fyada, \xe2hiret ve hakikat [[nokta-i nazar\u0131nda|bak\u0131\u015f a\xe7\u0131s\u0131nda]] olan [[h\xfcs\xfcn|g\xfczellik]] ve [[kubuh|\xe7irkinlik]] [[zat\xeedir|\xf6z\xfcndedir/kendindendir]]; emir ve [[nehy-i \u0130lah\xee|\u0130lahi yasak]] ona [[tabidir|uymaktad\u0131r]].\u201d Bu mezhebe g\xf6re insan, her i\u015fledi\u011fi amelde \u015f\xf6yle bir vesvese gelir: \u201cAcaba amelim [[nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirdeki|i\u015fin asl\u0131ndaki/ger\xe7ekteki]] g\xfczel [[surette|bi\xe7imde]] yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015f m\u0131d\u0131r?\u201d"},{"pageId":6,"rawText":"Amma mezheb-i hak olan Ehl-i S\xfcnnet ve Cemaat derler ki: Cenab-\u0131 Hak bir \u015feye emreder, sonra hasen olur. Nehyeder, sonra kabih olur. Demek emir ile g\xfczellik, nehiy ile \xe7irkinlik tahakkuk eder. H\xfcs\xfcn ve kubuh m\xfckellefin \u0131tt\u0131la\u0131na bakar ve ona g\xf6re takarrur eder. \u015eu h\xfcs\xfcn ve kubuh ise sur\xee ve d\xfcnyaya bakan y\xfcz\xfcnde de\u011fil belki \xe2hirete bakan y\xfczdedir.\\n\\nMesela, sen namaz k\u0131ld\u0131n veya abdest ald\u0131n. Halbuki namaz\u0131n\u0131 ve abdestini fesada verecek bir sebep, nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirde varm\u0131\u015f. L\xe2kin sen ona hi\xe7 muttali olmad\u0131n. Senin namaz\u0131n ve abdestin hem sahihtir hem hasendir. Mutezile der: \u201cHakikatte kabih ve f\xe2siddir. L\xe2kin senden kabul edilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc cehlin var, bilmedin ve \xf6zr\xfcn var.\u201d \xd6yle ise Ehl-i S\xfcnnet mezhebine g\xf6re, zahir-i \u015feriata muvaf\u0131k olarak i\u015fledi\u011fin ameline: \u201cAcaba sahih olmu\u015f mu?\u201d deyip vesvese etme. Fakat \u201cKabul olmu\u015f mu?\u201d de; gururlanma, ucbe girme.\\n\\n\u0130kinci merhem: Dinde harec yoktur. \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 Madem d\xf6rt mezhep hakt\u0131r. Madem isti\u011ffara m\xfcncer olan derk-i kusur ise gurura m\xfcncer olan h\xfcsn-\xfc amelin r\xfc\u2019yetine \u2013b\xf6yle vesveseli adama\u2013 m\xfcreccaht\u0131r. Yani b\xf6yle vesveseli adam, amelini g\xfczel g\xf6r\xfcp gurura d\xfc\u015fmektense amelini kusurlu g\xf6rse, isti\u011ffar etse daha evl\xe2d\u0131r.\\n\\nMadem b\xf6yledir, sen vesveseyi at. \u015eeytana de ki: \u015eu hal, bir harecdir. Hakikat-i hale muttali olmak g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Dindeki y\xfcsre m\xfcnaf\xeedir. \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650 \xa7 \u0627\u064e\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f \u064a\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064c esas\u0131na muhaliftir. Elbette b\xf6yle amelim bir mezheb-i hakka muvaf\u0131k gelir. O bana k\xe2fidir. Hem l\xe2ekall ben aczimi itiraf ederek ibadeti l\xe2y\u0131k-\u0131 vechile eda edemedi\u011fimden isti\u011ffar ve tazarru ile merhamet-i \u0130lahiyeye dehalet edip kusurum affolunmak, kusurlu amelim kabul olunmak i\xe7in m\xfctezellilane bir niyaza vesiledir.\\n\\nBe\u015finci Vecih\\n\\nMesail-i imaniyede \u015f\xfcphe suretinde gelen vesvesedir. B\xee\xe7are vesveseli adam, bazen tahayy\xfcl\xfc, taakkul ile iltibas eder. Yani hayale gelen bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, akla girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe tevehh\xfcm edip itikad\u0131na halel gelmi\u015f zanneder. Hem bazen tevehh\xfcm etti\u011fi bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, imana zarar veren bir \u015fek zanneder. Hem bazen tasavvur etti\u011fi bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, tasdik-i akl\xeeye girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe zanneder. Hem bazen bir emr-i k\xfcfr\xeede tefekk\xfcr\xfc, k\xfcf\xfcr zanneder. Yani dalaletin esbab\u0131n\u0131 anlamak suretinde kuvve-i m\xfcfekkirenin cevelan\u0131n\u0131 ve tetkikat\u0131n\u0131 ve b\xeetarafane muhakemesini, hilaf-\u0131 iman zanneder.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte telkinat-\u0131 \u015feytaniyenin eseri olan \u015fu zanlardan \xfcrkerek \u201cEyvah! Kalbim bozulmu\u015f, itikad\u0131ma halel gelmi\u015f.\u201d der. O haller, galiben ihtiyars\u0131z oldu\u011fundan c\xfcz-i ihtiyar\xeesiyle \u0131slah edemedi\u011finden yeise d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\nTahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr, k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi tevehh\xfcm-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr dahi k\xfcf\xfcr de\u011fildir. Tasavvur-u dalalet, dalalet olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi tefekk\xfcr-\xfc dalalet dahi dalalet de\u011fildir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hem tahayy\xfcl hem tevehh\xfcm hem tasavvur hem tefekk\xfcr; tasdik-i akl\xeeden ve iz\u2019an-\u0131 kalb\xeeden ayr\u0131d\u0131rlar, ba\u015fkad\u0131rlar. Onlar bir derece serbesttirler. C\xfcz-i ihtiyariyeyi pek dinlemiyorlar. Teklif-i din\xee alt\u0131na \xe7ok giremiyorlar. Tasdik ve iz\u2019an, \xf6yle de\u011filler. Bir mizana tabidirler. Hem tahayy\xfcl, tevehh\xfcm, tasavvur, tefekk\xfcr nas\u0131l ki tasdik ve iz\u2019an de\u011filler. \xd6yle de \u015f\xfcphe ve teredd\xfct say\u0131lmazlar. Fakat e\u011fer l\xfczumsuz tekrar ede ede m\xfcstekar bir hale gelse o vakit hakiki bir nevi \u015f\xfcphe, ondan tevell\xfcd edebilir. Hem b\xeetarafane muhakeme nam\u0131yla veya insaf nam\u0131na deyip \u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi iltizam ede ede, t\xe2 \xf6yle bir hale gelir ki ihtiyars\u0131z taraf-\u0131 muhalifi iltizam eder. Ona v\xe2cib olan hakk\u0131n iltizam\u0131 k\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r. O da tehlikeye d\xfc\u015fer. Hasm\u0131n veya \u015feytan\u0131n bir vekil-i fuzul\xeesi olacak bir halet, zihninde takarrur eder.","modernText":"[[Ancak/Fakat|Amma|]] [[hak mezhep|mezheb-i hak|]] olan [[Peygamberin s\xfcnnetine ve ashab\u0131n\u0131n yoluna uyan cemaat|Ehl-i S\xfcnnet ve Cemaat|]] derler ki: [[Y\xfcce Allah|Cenab-\u0131 Hak|]] bir \u015feye emreder, sonra [[g\xfczel/iyi|hasen|]] olur. [[Yasaklar|Nehyeder|]], sonra [[\xe7irkin/k\xf6t\xfc|kabih|]] olur. Demek emir ile g\xfczellik, [[yasak|nehiy|]] ile \xe7irkinlik [[ger\xe7ekle\u015fir/ortaya \xe7\u0131kar|tahakkuk eder|]]. [[G\xfczellik|H\xfcs\xfcn|]] ve [[\xe7irkinlik|kubuh|]] [[sorumlu ki\u015finin|m\xfckellefin|]] [[bilgisine/\xf6\u011frenmesine|\u0131tt\u0131la\u0131na|]] bakar ve ona g\xf6re [[kararla\u015f\u0131r/sabit olur|takarrur eder|]]. \u015eu [[g\xfczellik|h\xfcs\xfcn|]] ve [[\xe7irkinlik|kubuh|]] ise [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte|sur\xee|]] ve d\xfcnyaya bakan y\xfcz\xfcnde de\u011fil [[aksine/bilakis|belki|]] \xe2hirete bakan y\xfczdedir.\\n\\nMesela, sen namaz k\u0131ld\u0131n veya abdest ald\u0131n. Halbuki namaz\u0131n\u0131 ve abdestini [[bozulmaya|fesada|]] verecek bir sebep, [[i\u015fin asl\u0131nda/hakikatte|nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirde|]] varm\u0131\u015f. [[Fakat/Ancak|L\xe2kin|]] sen ona hi\xe7 [[vak\u0131f/haberdar|muttali|]] olmad\u0131n. Senin namaz\u0131n ve abdestin hem [[ge\xe7erlidir|sahihtir|]] hem [[g\xfczeldir|hasendir|]]. [[Kaderi inkar eden mezhep|Mutezile|]] der: \u201cHakikatte [[\xe7irkin|kabih|]] ve [[bozuktur/ge\xe7ersizdir|f\xe2siddir|]]. [[Fakat|L\xe2kin|]] senden kabul edilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[cahilli\u011fin/bilgisizli\u011fin|cehlin|]] var, bilmedin ve \xf6zr\xfcn var.\u201d \xd6yle ise Ehl-i S\xfcnnet mezhebine g\xf6re, [[\u015feriat\u0131n g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcrdeki h\xfckm\xfcne|zahir-i \u015feriata|]] [[uygun|muvaf\u0131k|]] olarak i\u015fledi\u011fin ameline: \u201cAcaba [[ge\xe7erli|sahih|]] olmu\u015f mu?\u201d deyip vesvese etme. Fakat \u201cKabul olmu\u015f mu?\u201d de; gururlanma, [[kendini be\u011fenmi\u015fli\u011fe|ucbe|]] girme.\\n\\n\u0130kinci merhem: Dinde [[zorluk/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131|harec|]] yoktur. [[Dinde zorluk yoktur.|\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|]] Madem d\xf6rt mezhep hakt\u0131r. Madem [[ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilemeye/t\xf6vbe etmeye|isti\u011ffara|]] [[g\xf6t\xfcren/sonu\xe7lanan|m\xfcncer olan|]] [[kusuru anlamak/fark etmek|derk-i kusur|]] ise gurura [[g\xf6t\xfcren/sonu\xe7lanan|m\xfcncer olan|]] [[g\xfczel amelin|h\xfcsn-\xfc amelin|]] [[g\xf6r\xfclmesine|r\xfc\u2019yetine|]] \u2013b\xf6yle vesveseli adama\u2013 [[tercih edilir/\xfcst\xfcnd\xfcr|m\xfcreccaht\u0131r|]]. Yani b\xf6yle vesveseli adam, amelini g\xfczel g\xf6r\xfcp gurura d\xfc\u015fmektense amelini kusurlu g\xf6rse, [[t\xf6vbe etse/ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilese|isti\u011ffar etse|]] daha [[iyidir/hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r|evl\xe2d\u0131r|]].\\n\\nMadem b\xf6yledir, sen vesveseyi at. \u015eeytana de ki: \u015eu hal, bir [[zorluktur/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131d\u0131r|harecdir|]]. [[Durumun ger\xe7e\u011fine/\u0130\u015fin asl\u0131na|Hakikat-i hale|]] [[vak\u0131f olmak/bilmek|muttali olmak|]] g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Dindeki [[kolayl\u0131\u011fa|y\xfcsre|]] [[z\u0131tt\u0131r/ayk\u0131r\u0131d\u0131r|m\xfcnaf\xeedir|]]. [[Dinde zorluk yoktur.|\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|]] \xa7 [[Din kolayl\u0131kt\u0131r.|\u0627\u064e\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f \u064a\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064c|Hadis-i \u015eerif]] esas\u0131na [[ayk\u0131r\u0131d\u0131r|muhaliftir|]]. Elbette b\xf6yle amelim bir [[hak mezhebe|mezheb-i hakka|]] [[uygun|muvaf\u0131k|]] gelir. O bana [[yeterlidir|k\xe2fidir|]]. Hem [[hi\xe7 olmazsa/en az\u0131ndan|l\xe2ekall|]] ben [[g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfc\u011f\xfcm\xfc|aczimi|]] itiraf ederek ibadeti [[lay\u0131k\u0131yla/gere\u011fi gibi|l\xe2y\u0131k-\u0131 vechile|]] [[yerine getiremedi\u011fimden|eda edemedi\u011fimden|]] [[ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dileme|isti\u011ffar|]] ve [[yalvarma|tazarru|]] ile [[\u0130lahi merhamete|merhamet-i \u0130lahiyeye|]] [[s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131p|dehalet edip|]] kusurum affolunmak, kusurlu amelim kabul olunmak i\xe7in [[ezilip b\xfcz\xfclerek/al\xe7akg\xf6n\xfcll\xfcl\xfckle|m\xfctezellilane|]] bir [[yalvar\u0131\u015fa/duaya|niyaza|]] vesiledir.\\n\\nBe\u015finci [[Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz|Vecih|]]\\n\\n[[\u0130man meselelerinde/konular\u0131nda|Mesail-i imaniyede|]] \u015f\xfcphe suretinde gelen vesvesedir. [[\xc7aresiz/Zavall\u0131|B\xee\xe7are|]] vesveseli adam, bazen [[hayal etmeyi|tahayy\xfcl\xfc|]], [[ak\u0131l y\xfcr\xfctme/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme|taakkul|]] ile [[kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r|iltibas eder|]]. Yani hayale gelen bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, akla girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe [[zannedip/kuruntu edip|tevehh\xfcm edip|]] [[inanc\u0131na|itikad\u0131na|]] [[bozukluk/zarar|halel|]] gelmi\u015f zanneder. Hem bazen [[kuruntu etti\u011fi/vehimlendi\u011fi|tevehh\xfcm etti\u011fi|]] bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, imana zarar veren bir [[\u015f\xfcphe/teredd\xfct|\u015fek|]] zanneder. Hem bazen [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc/zihninde \u015fekillendirdi\u011fi|tasavvur etti\u011fi|]] bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, [[akl\u0131n onay\u0131na/kabul\xfcne|tasdik-i akl\xeeye|]] girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe zanneder. Hem bazen bir [[k\xfcf\xfcr olan \u015feyde/inkarda|emr-i k\xfcfr\xeede|]] [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmeyi|tefekk\xfcr\xfc|]], k\xfcf\xfcr zanneder. Yani [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n/do\u011fru yoldan \xe7\u0131kman\u0131n|dalaletin|]] [[sebeplerini|esbab\u0131n\u0131|]] anlamak suretinde [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme g\xfcc\xfcn\xfcn|kuvve-i m\xfcfekkirenin|]] [[dola\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131/hareketini|cevelan\u0131n\u0131|]] ve [[incelemesini|tetkikat\u0131n\u0131|]] ve [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] [[de\u011ferlendirmesini|muhakemesini|]], [[imana ayk\u0131r\u0131|hilaf-\u0131 iman|]] zanneder.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[\u015feytan\u0131n telkinlerinin/f\u0131s\u0131ldamalar\u0131n\u0131n|telkinat-\u0131 \u015feytaniyenin|]] eseri olan \u015fu zanlardan \xfcrkerek \u201cEyvah! Kalbim bozulmu\u015f, [[inanc\u0131ma|itikad\u0131ma|]] [[zarar/bozukluk|halel|]] gelmi\u015f.\u201d der. O haller, [[\xe7o\u011funlukla|galiben|]] [[istemsiz/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131|ihtiyars\u0131z|]] oldu\u011fundan [[k\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131 iradesiyle/se\xe7me g\xfcc\xfcyle|c\xfcz-i ihtiyar\xeesiyle|]] [[d\xfczeltemedi\u011finden|\u0131slah edemedi\u011finden|]] [[\xfcmitsizli\u011fe|yeise|]] d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[K\xfcfr\xfc hayal etmek|Tahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|]], k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[k\xfcfr\xfc vehmetmek/kuruntu etmek|tevehh\xfcm-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|]] dahi k\xfcf\xfcr de\u011fildir. [[Sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmek/tasavvur etmek|Tasavvur-u dalalet|]], [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131k|dalalet|]] olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 tefekk\xfcr etmek/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmek|tefekk\xfcr-\xfc dalalet|]] dahi [[sapk\u0131nl\u0131k|dalalet|]] de\u011fildir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hem [[hayal etme|tahayy\xfcl|]] hem [[vehmetme/kuruntu etme|tevehh\xfcm|]] hem [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme/zihinde \u015fekillendirme|tasavvur|]] hem [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme|tefekk\xfcr|]]; [[akl\u0131n onay\u0131ndan|tasdik-i akl\xeeden|]] ve [[kalbin kesin inanc\u0131ndan/kabul\xfcnden|iz\u2019an-\u0131 kalb\xeeden|]] ayr\u0131d\u0131rlar, ba\u015fkad\u0131rlar. Onlar bir derece serbesttirler. [[K\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131 iradeyi|C\xfcz-i ihtiyariyeyi|]] pek dinlemiyorlar. [[Dini y\xfck\xfcml\xfcl\xfck|Teklif-i din\xee|]] alt\u0131na \xe7ok giremiyorlar. Tasdik ve [[kesin inan\xe7|iz\u2019an|]], \xf6yle de\u011filler. Bir [[\xf6l\xe7\xfcye/teraziye|mizana|]] [[ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131rlar|tabidirler|]]. Hem [[hayal etme|tahayy\xfcl|]], [[vehmetme|tevehh\xfcm|]], [[tasarlama|tasavvur|]], [[d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme|tefekk\xfcr|]] nas\u0131l ki tasdik ve [[kesin inan\xe7|iz\u2019an|]] de\u011filler. \xd6yle de \u015f\xfcphe ve teredd\xfct say\u0131lmazlar. Fakat e\u011fer l\xfczumsuz tekrar ede ede [[kararl\u0131/yerle\u015fmi\u015f|m\xfcstekar|]] bir hale gelse o vakit [[ger\xe7ek|hakiki|]] bir [[t\xfcr|nevi|]] \u015f\xfcphe, ondan [[do\u011fabilir/t\xfcreyebilir|tevell\xfcd edebilir|]]. Hem [[tarafs\u0131zca|b\xeetarafane|]] [[yarg\u0131lama/de\u011ferlendirme|muhakeme|]] [[ad\u0131yla|nam\u0131yla|]] veya insaf [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] deyip [[kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131/muhalif \u015f\u0131kk\u0131|\u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi|]] [[taraftar ola ola/gerekli g\xf6re g\xf6re|iltizam ede ede|]], t\xe2 \xf6yle bir hale gelir ki [[istemsizce/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131|ihtiyars\u0131z|]] [[kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131|taraf-\u0131 muhalifi|]] [[tutar/benimser|iltizam eder|]]. Ona [[gerekli|v\xe2cib|]] olan hakk\u0131n [[taraftarl\u0131\u011f\u0131/savunulmas\u0131|iltizam\u0131|]] k\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r. O da tehlikeye d\xfc\u015fer. [[D\xfc\u015fman\u0131n|Hasm\u0131n|]] veya \u015feytan\u0131n bir [[yetkisiz vekili/gereksiz temsilcisi|vekil-i fuzul\xeesi|]] olacak bir [[durum/hal|halet|]], zihninde [[yerle\u015fir/karar k\u0131lar|takarrur eder|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:46","oldText":"[[Amma|Ancak/Fakat]] [[mezheb-i hak|hak mezhep]] olan [[Ehl-i S\xfcnnet ve Cemaat|Peygamberin s\xfcnnetine ve ashab\u0131n\u0131n yoluna uyan cemaat]] derler ki: [[Cenab-\u0131 Hak|Y\xfcce Allah]] bir \u015feye emreder, sonra [[hasen|g\xfczel/iyi]] olur. [[Nehyeder|Yasaklar]], sonra [[kabih|\xe7irkin/k\xf6t\xfc]] olur. Demek emir ile g\xfczellik, [[nehiy|yasak]] ile \xe7irkinlik [[tahakkuk eder|ger\xe7ekle\u015fir/ortaya \xe7\u0131kar]]. [[H\xfcs\xfcn|G\xfczellik]] ve [[kubuh|\xe7irkinlik]] [[m\xfckellefin|sorumlu ki\u015finin]] [[\u0131tt\u0131la\u0131na|bilgisine/\xf6\u011frenmesine]] bakar ve ona g\xf6re [[takarrur eder|kararla\u015f\u0131r/sabit olur]]. \u015eu [[h\xfcs\xfcn|g\xfczellik]] ve [[kubuh|\xe7irkinlik]] ise [[sur\xee|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte]] ve d\xfcnyaya bakan y\xfcz\xfcnde de\u011fil [[belki|aksine/bilakis]] \xe2hirete bakan y\xfczdedir.\\n\\nMesela, sen namaz k\u0131ld\u0131n veya abdest ald\u0131n. Halbuki namaz\u0131n\u0131 ve abdestini [[fesada|bozulmaya]] verecek bir sebep, [[nefs\xfc\u2019l-emirde|i\u015fin asl\u0131nda/hakikatte]] varm\u0131\u015f. [[L\xe2kin|Fakat/Ancak]] sen ona hi\xe7 [[muttali|vak\u0131f/haberdar]] olmad\u0131n. Senin namaz\u0131n ve abdestin hem [[sahihtir|ge\xe7erlidir]] hem [[hasendir|g\xfczeldir]]. [[Mutezile|Kaderi inkar eden mezhep]] der: \u201cHakikatte [[kabih|\xe7irkin]] ve [[f\xe2siddir|bozuktur/ge\xe7ersizdir]]. [[L\xe2kin|Fakat]] senden kabul edilir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[cehlin|cahilli\u011fin/bilgisizli\u011fin]] var, bilmedin ve \xf6zr\xfcn var.\u201d \xd6yle ise Ehl-i S\xfcnnet mezhebine g\xf6re, [[zahir-i \u015feriata|\u015feriat\u0131n g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcrdeki h\xfckm\xfcne]] [[muvaf\u0131k|uygun]] olarak i\u015fledi\u011fin ameline: \u201cAcaba [[sahih|ge\xe7erli]] olmu\u015f mu?\u201d deyip vesvese etme. Fakat \u201cKabul olmu\u015f mu?\u201d de; gururlanma, [[ucbe|kendini be\u011fenmi\u015fli\u011fe]] girme.\\n\\n\u0130kinci merhem: Dinde [[harec|zorluk/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131]] yoktur. [[\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|Dinde zorluk yoktur.]] Madem d\xf6rt mezhep hakt\u0131r. Madem [[isti\u011ffara|ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilemeye/t\xf6vbe etmeye]] [[m\xfcncer olan|g\xf6t\xfcren/sonu\xe7lanan]] [[derk-i kusur|kusuru anlamak/fark etmek]] ise gurura [[m\xfcncer olan|g\xf6t\xfcren/sonu\xe7lanan]] [[h\xfcsn-\xfc amelin|g\xfczel amelin]] [[r\xfc\u2019yetine|g\xf6r\xfclmesine]] \u2013b\xf6yle vesveseli adama\u2013 [[m\xfcreccaht\u0131r|tercih edilir/\xfcst\xfcnd\xfcr]]. Yani b\xf6yle vesveseli adam, amelini g\xfczel g\xf6r\xfcp gurura d\xfc\u015fmektense amelini kusurlu g\xf6rse, [[isti\u011ffar etse|t\xf6vbe etse/ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilese]] daha [[evl\xe2d\u0131r|iyidir/hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r]].\\n\\nMadem b\xf6yledir, sen vesveseyi at. \u015eeytana de ki: \u015eu hal, bir [[harecdir|zorluktur/s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131d\u0131r]]. [[Hakikat-i hale|Durumun ger\xe7e\u011fine/\u0130\u015fin asl\u0131na]] [[muttali olmak|vak\u0131f olmak/bilmek]] g\xfc\xe7t\xfcr. Dindeki [[y\xfcsre|kolayl\u0131\u011fa]] [[m\xfcnaf\xeedir|z\u0131tt\u0131r/ayk\u0131r\u0131d\u0131r]]. [[\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0641\u0650\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u0650|Dinde zorluk yoktur.]] \xa7 [[\u0627\u064e\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064f \u064a\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064c|Din kolayl\u0131kt\u0131r.|Hadis-i \u015eerif]] esas\u0131na [[muhaliftir|ayk\u0131r\u0131d\u0131r]]. Elbette b\xf6yle amelim bir [[mezheb-i hakka|hak mezhebe]] [[muvaf\u0131k|uygun]] gelir. O bana [[k\xe2fidir|yeterlidir]]. Hem [[l\xe2ekall|hi\xe7 olmazsa/en az\u0131ndan]] ben [[aczimi|g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfc\u011f\xfcm\xfc]] itiraf ederek ibadeti [[l\xe2y\u0131k-\u0131 vechile|lay\u0131k\u0131yla/gere\u011fi gibi]] [[eda edemedi\u011fimden|yerine getiremedi\u011fimden]] [[isti\u011ffar|ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dileme]] ve [[tazarru|yalvarma]] ile [[merhamet-i \u0130lahiyeye|\u0130lahi merhamete]] [[dehalet edip|s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131p]] kusurum affolunmak, kusurlu amelim kabul olunmak i\xe7in [[m\xfctezellilane|ezilip b\xfcz\xfclerek/al\xe7akg\xf6n\xfcll\xfcl\xfckle]] bir [[niyaza|yalvar\u0131\u015fa/duaya]] vesiledir.\\n\\nBe\u015finci [[Vecih|Y\xf6n/Y\xfcz]]\\n\\n[[Mesail-i imaniyede|\u0130man meselelerinde/konular\u0131nda]] \u015f\xfcphe suretinde gelen vesvesedir. [[B\xee\xe7are|\xc7aresiz/Zavall\u0131]] vesveseli adam, bazen [[tahayy\xfcl\xfc|hayal etmeyi]], [[taakkul|ak\u0131l y\xfcr\xfctme/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme]] ile [[iltibas eder|kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r]]. Yani hayale gelen bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, akla girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe [[tevehh\xfcm edip|zannedip/kuruntu edip]] [[itikad\u0131na|inanc\u0131na]] [[halel|bozukluk/zarar]] gelmi\u015f zanneder. Hem bazen [[tevehh\xfcm etti\u011fi|kuruntu etti\u011fi/vehimlendi\u011fi]] bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, imana zarar veren bir [[\u015fek|\u015f\xfcphe/teredd\xfct]] zanneder. Hem bazen [[tasavvur etti\u011fi|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnd\xfc\u011f\xfc/zihninde \u015fekillendirdi\u011fi]] bir \u015f\xfcpheyi, [[tasdik-i akl\xeeye|akl\u0131n onay\u0131na/kabul\xfcne]] girmi\u015f bir \u015f\xfcphe zanneder. Hem bazen bir [[emr-i k\xfcfr\xeede|k\xfcf\xfcr olan \u015feyde/inkarda]] [[tefekk\xfcr\xfc|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmeyi]], k\xfcf\xfcr zanneder. Yani [[dalaletin|sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131n/do\u011fru yoldan \xe7\u0131kman\u0131n]] [[esbab\u0131n\u0131|sebeplerini]] anlamak suretinde [[kuvve-i m\xfcfekkirenin|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme g\xfcc\xfcn\xfcn]] [[cevelan\u0131n\u0131|dola\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131/hareketini]] ve [[tetkikat\u0131n\u0131|incelemesini]] ve [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakemesini|de\u011ferlendirmesini]], [[hilaf-\u0131 iman|imana ayk\u0131r\u0131]] zanneder.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte [[telkinat-\u0131 \u015feytaniyenin|\u015feytan\u0131n telkinlerinin/f\u0131s\u0131ldamalar\u0131n\u0131n]] eseri olan \u015fu zanlardan \xfcrkerek \u201cEyvah! Kalbim bozulmu\u015f, [[itikad\u0131ma|inanc\u0131ma]] [[halel|zarar/bozukluk]] gelmi\u015f.\u201d der. O haller, [[galiben|\xe7o\u011funlukla]] [[ihtiyars\u0131z|istemsiz/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131]] oldu\u011fundan [[c\xfcz-i ihtiyar\xeesiyle|k\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131 iradesiyle/se\xe7me g\xfcc\xfcyle]] [[\u0131slah edemedi\u011finden|d\xfczeltemedi\u011finden]] [[yeise|\xfcmitsizli\u011fe]] d\xfc\u015fer.\\n\\nBu yaran\u0131n merhemi \u015fudur ki:\\n\\n[[Tahayy\xfcl-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|K\xfcfr\xfc hayal etmek]], k\xfcf\xfcr olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[tevehh\xfcm-\xfc k\xfcf\xfcr|k\xfcfr\xfc vehmetmek/kuruntu etmek]] dahi k\xfcf\xfcr de\u011fildir. [[Tasavvur-u dalalet|Sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmek/tasavvur etmek]], [[dalalet|sapk\u0131nl\u0131k]] olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi [[tefekk\xfcr-\xfc dalalet|sapk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 tefekk\xfcr etmek/d\xfc\u015f\xfcnmek]] dahi [[dalalet|sapk\u0131nl\u0131k]] de\u011fildir. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hem [[tahayy\xfcl|hayal etme]] hem [[tevehh\xfcm|vehmetme/kuruntu etme]] hem [[tasavvur|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme/zihinde \u015fekillendirme]] hem [[tefekk\xfcr|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme]]; [[tasdik-i akl\xeeden|akl\u0131n onay\u0131ndan]] ve [[iz\u2019an-\u0131 kalb\xeeden|kalbin kesin inanc\u0131ndan/kabul\xfcnden]] ayr\u0131d\u0131rlar, ba\u015fkad\u0131rlar. Onlar bir derece serbesttirler. [[C\xfcz-i ihtiyariyeyi|K\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131 iradeyi]] pek dinlemiyorlar. [[Teklif-i din\xee|Dini y\xfck\xfcml\xfcl\xfck]] alt\u0131na \xe7ok giremiyorlar. Tasdik ve [[iz\u2019an|kesin inan\xe7]], \xf6yle de\u011filler. Bir [[mizana|\xf6l\xe7\xfcye/teraziye]] [[tabidirler|ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131rlar]]. Hem [[tahayy\xfcl|hayal etme]], [[tevehh\xfcm|vehmetme]], [[tasavvur|tasarlama]], [[tefekk\xfcr|d\xfc\u015f\xfcnme]] nas\u0131l ki tasdik ve [[iz\u2019an|kesin inan\xe7]] de\u011filler. \xd6yle de \u015f\xfcphe ve teredd\xfct say\u0131lmazlar. Fakat e\u011fer l\xfczumsuz tekrar ede ede [[m\xfcstekar|kararl\u0131/yerle\u015fmi\u015f]] bir hale gelse o vakit [[hakiki|ger\xe7ek]] bir [[nevi|t\xfcr]] \u015f\xfcphe, ondan [[tevell\xfcd edebilir|do\u011fabilir/t\xfcreyebilir]]. Hem [[b\xeetarafane|tarafs\u0131zca]] [[muhakeme|yarg\u0131lama/de\u011ferlendirme]] [[nam\u0131yla|ad\u0131yla]] veya insaf [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] deyip [[\u015f\u0131kk-\u0131 muhalifi|kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131/muhalif \u015f\u0131kk\u0131]] [[iltizam ede ede|taraftar ola ola/gerekli g\xf6re g\xf6re]], t\xe2 \xf6yle bir hale gelir ki [[ihtiyars\u0131z|istemsizce/irade d\u0131\u015f\u0131]] [[taraf-\u0131 muhalifi|kar\u015f\u0131 taraf\u0131]] [[iltizam eder|tutar/benimser]]. Ona [[v\xe2cib|gerekli]] olan hakk\u0131n [[iltizam\u0131|taraftarl\u0131\u011f\u0131/savunulmas\u0131]] k\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r. O da tehlikeye d\xfc\u015fer. [[Hasm\u0131n|D\xfc\u015fman\u0131n]] veya \u015feytan\u0131n bir [[vekil-i fuzul\xeesi|yetkisiz vekili/gereksiz temsilcisi]] olacak bir [[halet|durum/hal]], zihninde [[takarrur eder|yerle\u015fir/karar k\u0131lar]]."},{"pageId":7,"rawText":"\u015eu nevi vesvesenin en m\xfchimmi budur ki: Vesveseli adam, imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee ile imk\xe2n-\u0131 zihn\xeeyi birbiriyle iltibas eder. Yani bir \u015feyi zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6rse o \u015feyi zihnen dahi m\xfcmk\xfcn ve aklen me\u015fkuk tevehh\xfcm eder. Halbuki ilm-i kel\xe2m\u0131n kaidelerindendir ki imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee ise yak\xeen-i ilm\xeeye m\xfcnaf\xee de\u011fil ve zaruret-i zihniyeye z\u0131ddiyeti yoktur. Mesela, \u015fu dakikada Karadeniz\u2019in yere batmas\u0131, zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ve o imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee ile muhtemeldir. Halbuki yak\xeenen, o denizin yerinde oldu\u011funu h\xfckmediyoruz, \u015f\xfcphesiz biliyoruz. Ve o ihtimal-i imk\xe2n\xee ve o imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee, bize \u015fek vermez, bir \u015f\xfcphe getirmez, yak\xeenimizi bozmaz. Mesela, \u015fu g\xfcne\u015f zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ki bug\xfcn gur\xfbb etmesin veya yar\u0131n tul\xfb etmesin. Halbuki bu imk\xe2n yak\xeenimize zarar vermez, \u015f\xfcphe getirmez.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bunun gibi mesela, hakaik-i imaniyeden olan hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin gur\xfbbuna ve hayat-\u0131 uhreviyenin tul\xfbuna, imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee cihetinde gelen vehimler, yak\xeen-i iman\xeeye zarar vermez. Hem \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u062d\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0626\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064d yani \u201cBir delilden ne\u015f\u2019et etmeyen bir ihtimalin hi\xe7 ehemmiyeti yoktur.\u201d olan kaide-i me\u015fhure hem us\xfbl\xfc\u2019d-din hem us\xfbl\xfc\u2019l-f\u0131kh\u0131n kaide-i mukarreresindendir.\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: Bu derece m\xfc\u2019minlere muz\u0131r ve m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7 olan vesvese, ne hikmete binaen bize bela olmu\u015f?\\n\\nElcevap: \u0130frata varmamak hem galebe \xe7almamak \u015fart\u0131yla asl-\u0131 vesvese; teyakkuza sebeptir, taharriye d\xe2\xeedir, ciddiyete vesiledir. L\xe2kaytl\u0131\u011f\u0131 atar, tehav\xfcn\xfc def\u2019eder. Onun i\xe7in Hak\xeem-i Mutlak, \u015fu d\xe2r-\u0131 imtihanda, \u015fu meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabakada bize bir kam\xe7\u0131-y\u0131 te\u015fvik olarak vesveseyi \u015feytan\u0131n eline vermi\u015f. Be\u015ferin ba\u015f\u0131na vuruyor. \u015eayet ziyade incitse Hak\xeem-i Rah\xeem\u2019e \u015fekva etmeli \u200c\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062c\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\u200c demeli.\\n\\n***\\n\\n[1] H\xe2\u015fiye: Bu makam, bir ba\u011fda bir zata bir derstir ki bu tarz ile beyan edilmi\u015f.","modernText":"\u015eu [[\xe7e\u015fit/t\xfcr|nevi|]] vesvesenin en [[\xf6nemlisi|m\xfchimmi|]] budur ki: Vesveseli adam, [[zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|bir \u015feyin kendi \xf6z\xfcnde olabilme ihtimali]] ile [[zihnen m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6rmeyi|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zihn\xeeyi|aklen olabilir sanmay\u0131]] birbiriyle [[kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r|iltibas eder|]]. Yani bir \u015feyi [[\xf6z\xfcnde/kendi yap\u0131s\u0131nda|zat\u0131nda|]] m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6rse o \u015feyi zihnen dahi m\xfcmk\xfcn ve aklen [[\u015f\xfcpheli/ku\u015fkulu|me\u015fkuk|]] [[zanneder/kuruntu eder|tevehh\xfcm eder|]]. Halbuki [[kelam ilminin/inan\xe7 esaslar\u0131n\u0131 inceleyen ilmin|ilm-i kel\xe2m\u0131n|]] kaidelerindendir ki [[zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|]] ise [[ilmi kesinli\u011fe|yak\xeen-i ilm\xeeye|]] [[ayk\u0131r\u0131/z\u0131t|m\xfcnaf\xee|]] de\u011fil ve [[zihinsel zorunlulu\u011fa/akl\u0131n kesin kabul\xfcne|zaruret-i zihniyeye|]] [[z\u0131tl\u0131\u011f\u0131/kar\u015f\u0131tl\u0131\u011f\u0131|z\u0131ddiyeti|]] yoktur. Mesela, \u015fu dakikada Karadeniz\u2019in yere batmas\u0131, [[\xf6z\xfcnde|zat\u0131nda|]] m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ve o [[zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|]] ile [[ihtimal dahilindedir|muhtemeldir|]]. Halbuki [[kesin olarak/\u015f\xfcphesizce|yak\xeenen|]], o denizin yerinde oldu\u011funu [[h\xfck\xfcm veriyoruz/kabul ediyoruz|h\xfckmediyoruz|]], \u015f\xfcphesiz biliyoruz. Ve o [[olabilirlik ihtimali|ihtimal-i imk\xe2n\xee|]] ve o [[zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|]], bize [[\u015f\xfcphe/ku\u015fku|\u015fek|]] vermez, bir \u015f\xfcphe getirmez, [[kesin bilgimizi|yak\xeenimizi|]] bozmaz. Mesela, \u015fu g\xfcne\u015f [[\xf6z\xfcnde|zat\u0131nda|]] m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ki bug\xfcn [[batmas\u0131n|gur\xfbb etmesin|]] veya yar\u0131n [[do\u011fmas\u0131n|tul\xfb etmesin|]]. Halbuki bu imk\xe2n [[kesin bilgimize|yak\xeenimize|]] zarar vermez, \u015f\xfcphe getirmez.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bunun gibi mesela, [[iman hakikatlerinden|hakaik-i imaniyeden|]] olan [[d\xfcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131n|hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin|]] [[bat\u0131\u015f\u0131na/son bulmas\u0131na|gur\xfbbuna|]] ve [[ahiret hayat\u0131n\u0131n|hayat-\u0131 uhreviyenin|]] [[do\u011fu\u015funa/ba\u015flamas\u0131na|tul\xfbuna|]], [[zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|]] [[y\xf6n\xfcnde|cihetinde|]] gelen [[kuruntular/yersiz \u015f\xfcpheler|vehimler|]], [[iman\xee kesinli\u011fe/inan\xe7 sa\u011flaml\u0131\u011f\u0131na|yak\xeen-i iman\xeeye|]] zarar vermez. Hem [[Delilden kaynaklanmayan ihtimale itibar edilmez.|\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u062d\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0626\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064d|]] yani \u201cBir delilden [[do\u011fmayan/kaynaklanmayan|ne\u015f\u2019et etmeyen|]] bir ihtimalin hi\xe7 [[\xf6nemi|ehemmiyeti|]] yoktur.\u201d olan [[me\u015fhur kural|kaide-i me\u015fhure|]] hem [[din usul\xfc/kelam ilmi|us\xfbl\xfc\u2019d-din|]] hem [[f\u0131k\u0131h usul\xfcn\xfcn|us\xfbl\xfc\u2019l-f\u0131kh\u0131n|]] [[kararla\u015fm\u0131\u015f/yerle\u015fik kural\u0131ndand\u0131r|kaide-i mukarreresindendir|]].\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: Bu derece [[iman edenlere|m\xfc\u2019minlere|]] [[zararl\u0131|muz\u0131r|]] ve [[s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131 verici/rahats\u0131z edici|m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7|]] olan vesvese, ne [[hikmete dayanarak|hikmete binaen|]] bize bela olmu\u015f?\\n\\n[[Cevap|Elcevap|]]: [[a\u015f\u0131r\u0131l\u0131\u011fa|\u0130frata|]] varmamak hem [[\xfcst\xfcn gelmemek/hakim olmamak|galebe \xe7almamak|]] \u015fart\u0131yla [[vesvesenin asl\u0131|asl-\u0131 vesvese|]]; [[uyan\u0131kl\u0131\u011fa|teyakkuza|]] sebeptir, [[ara\u015ft\u0131rmaya|taharriye|]] [[davet\xe7idir/sebeptir|d\xe2\xeedir|]], ciddiyete [[arac\u0131d\u0131r|vesiledir|]]. [[ilgisizli\u011fi/duyars\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131|L\xe2kaytl\u0131\u011f\u0131|]] atar, [[gev\u015fekli\u011fi/\xf6nemsememeyi|tehav\xfcn\xfc|]] [[giderir/uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r|def\u2019eder|]]. Onun i\xe7in [[her i\u015fi hikmetli olan Allah|Hak\xeem-i Mutlak|]], \u015fu [[imtihan yurdunda|d\xe2r-\u0131 imtihanda|]], \u015fu [[yar\u0131\u015f meydan\u0131nda|meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabakada|]] bize bir [[te\u015fvik kam\xe7\u0131s\u0131|kam\xe7\u0131-y\u0131 te\u015fvik|]] olarak vesveseyi \u015feytan\u0131n eline vermi\u015f. [[insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|Be\u015ferin|]] ba\u015f\u0131na vuruyor. \u015eayet [[fazla/a\u015f\u0131r\u0131|ziyade|]] incitse [[hikmet ve merhamet sahibi Allah\'a|Hak\xeem-i Rah\xeem\u2019e|]] [[\u015fikayet etmeli/halini arz etmeli|\u015fekva etmeli|]] [[Kovulmu\u015f \u015feytandan Allah\'a s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m|\u200c\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062c\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\u200c|]] demeli.\\n\\n***\\n\\n[1] [[Dipnot|H\xe2\u015fiye|]]: Bu makam, bir ba\u011fda bir zata bir derstir ki bu tarz ile [[a\xe7\u0131klanm\u0131\u015f|beyan edilmi\u015f|]].","processedBy":"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.22-14:48","oldText":"\u015eu [[nevi|\xe7e\u015fit/t\xfcr]] vesvesenin en [[m\xfchimmi|\xf6nemlisi]] budur ki: Vesveseli adam, [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma|bir \u015feyin kendi \xf6z\xfcnde olabilme ihtimali]] ile [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zihn\xeeyi|zihnen m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6rmeyi|aklen olabilir sanmay\u0131]] birbiriyle [[iltibas eder|kar\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r]]. Yani bir \u015feyi [[zat\u0131nda|\xf6z\xfcnde/kendi yap\u0131s\u0131nda]] m\xfcmk\xfcn g\xf6rse o \u015feyi zihnen dahi m\xfcmk\xfcn ve aklen [[me\u015fkuk|\u015f\xfcpheli/ku\u015fkulu]] [[tevehh\xfcm eder|zanneder/kuruntu eder]]. Halbuki [[ilm-i kel\xe2m\u0131n|kelam ilminin/inan\xe7 esaslar\u0131n\u0131 inceleyen ilmin]] kaidelerindendir ki [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma]] ise [[yak\xeen-i ilm\xeeye|ilmi kesinli\u011fe]] [[m\xfcnaf\xee|ayk\u0131r\u0131/z\u0131t]] de\u011fil ve [[zaruret-i zihniyeye|zihinsel zorunlulu\u011fa/akl\u0131n kesin kabul\xfcne]] [[z\u0131ddiyeti|z\u0131tl\u0131\u011f\u0131/kar\u015f\u0131tl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] yoktur. Mesela, \u015fu dakikada Karadeniz\u2019in yere batmas\u0131, [[zat\u0131nda|\xf6z\xfcnde]] m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ve o [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma]] ile [[muhtemeldir|ihtimal dahilindedir]]. Halbuki [[yak\xeenen|kesin olarak/\u015f\xfcphesizce]], o denizin yerinde oldu\u011funu [[h\xfckmediyoruz|h\xfck\xfcm veriyoruz/kabul ediyoruz]], \u015f\xfcphesiz biliyoruz. Ve o [[ihtimal-i imk\xe2n\xee|olabilirlik ihtimali]] ve o [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma]], bize [[\u015fek|\u015f\xfcphe/ku\u015fku]] vermez, bir \u015f\xfcphe getirmez, [[yak\xeenimizi|kesin bilgimizi]] bozmaz. Mesela, \u015fu g\xfcne\u015f [[zat\u0131nda|\xf6z\xfcnde]] m\xfcmk\xfcnd\xfcr ki bug\xfcn [[gur\xfbb etmesin|batmas\u0131n]] veya yar\u0131n [[tul\xfb etmesin|do\u011fmas\u0131n]]. Halbuki bu imk\xe2n [[yak\xeenimize|kesin bilgimize]] zarar vermez, \u015f\xfcphe getirmez.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bunun gibi mesela, [[hakaik-i imaniyeden|iman hakikatlerinden]] olan [[hayat-\u0131 d\xfcnyeviyenin|d\xfcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131n]] [[gur\xfbbuna|bat\u0131\u015f\u0131na/son bulmas\u0131na]] ve [[hayat-\u0131 uhreviyenin|ahiret hayat\u0131n\u0131n]] [[tul\xfbuna|do\u011fu\u015funa/ba\u015flamas\u0131na]], [[imk\xe2n-\u0131 zat\xee|zat\u0131nda m\xfcmk\xfcn olma]] [[cihetinde|y\xf6n\xfcnde]] gelen [[vehimler|kuruntular/yersiz \u015f\xfcpheler]], [[yak\xeen-i iman\xeeye|iman\xee kesinli\u011fe/inan\xe7 sa\u011flaml\u0131\u011f\u0131na]] zarar vermez. Hem [[\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0627\u0650\u062d\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0626\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u0644\u0656\u064a\u0644\u064d|Delilden kaynaklanmayan ihtimale itibar edilmez.]] yani \u201cBir delilden [[ne\u015f\u2019et etmeyen|do\u011fmayan/kaynaklanmayan]] bir ihtimalin hi\xe7 [[ehemmiyeti|\xf6nemi]] yoktur.\u201d olan [[kaide-i me\u015fhure|me\u015fhur kural]] hem [[us\xfbl\xfc\u2019d-din|din usul\xfc/kelam ilmi]] hem [[us\xfbl\xfc\u2019l-f\u0131kh\u0131n|f\u0131k\u0131h usul\xfcn\xfcn]] [[kaide-i mukarreresindendir|kararla\u015fm\u0131\u015f/yerle\u015fik kural\u0131ndand\u0131r]].\\n\\nE\u011fer desen: Bu derece [[m\xfc\u2019minlere|iman edenlere]] [[muz\u0131r|zararl\u0131]] ve [[m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131 verici/rahats\u0131z edici]] olan vesvese, ne [[hikmete binaen|hikmete dayanarak]] bize bela olmu\u015f?\\n\\n[[Elcevap|Cevap]]: [[\u0130frata|a\u015f\u0131r\u0131l\u0131\u011fa]] varmamak hem [[galebe \xe7almamak|\xfcst\xfcn gelmemek/hakim olmamak]] \u015fart\u0131yla [[asl-\u0131 vesvese|vesvesenin asl\u0131]]; [[teyakkuza|uyan\u0131kl\u0131\u011fa]] sebeptir, [[taharriye|ara\u015ft\u0131rmaya]] [[d\xe2\xeedir|davet\xe7idir/sebeptir]], ciddiyete [[vesiledir|arac\u0131d\u0131r]]. [[L\xe2kaytl\u0131\u011f\u0131|ilgisizli\u011fi/duyars\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131]] atar, [[tehav\xfcn\xfc|gev\u015fekli\u011fi/\xf6nemsememeyi]] [[def\u2019eder|giderir/uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r]]. Onun i\xe7in [[Hak\xeem-i Mutlak|her i\u015fi hikmetli olan Allah]], \u015fu [[d\xe2r-\u0131 imtihanda|imtihan yurdunda]], \u015fu [[meydan-\u0131 m\xfcsabakada|yar\u0131\u015f meydan\u0131nda]] bize bir [[kam\xe7\u0131-y\u0131 te\u015fvik|te\u015fvik kam\xe7\u0131s\u0131]] olarak vesveseyi \u015feytan\u0131n eline vermi\u015f. [[Be\u015ferin|insanl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] ba\u015f\u0131na vuruyor. \u015eayet [[ziyade|fazla/a\u015f\u0131r\u0131]] incitse [[Hak\xeem-i Rah\xeem\u2019e|hikmet ve merhamet sahibi Allah\'a]] [[\u015fekva etmeli|\u015fikayet etmeli/halini arz etmeli]] [[\u200c\u0627\u064e\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0630\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062c\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\u200c|Kovulmu\u015f \u015feytandan Allah\'a s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131r\u0131m]] demeli.\\n\\n***\\n\\n[1] [[H\xe2\u015fiye|Dipnot]]: Bu makam, bir ba\u011fda bir zata bir derstir ki bu tarz ile [[beyan edilmi\u015f|a\xe7\u0131klanm\u0131\u015f]]."}]')}}]);